description:
Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and modern convenience in this 2023 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Custom. With its impressive 2.7L Turbo engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and 4-wheel drive, this truck is ready to take on any task you throw its way. Boasting a sleek gray exterior, this Silverado is not only stylish but also packed with an array of premium features that will elevate your driving experience.

• ALLOY WHEELS
• APPLE ANDROID CARPLAY
• BACKUP CAMERA
• KEYLESS ENTRY
• PUSH BUTTON START
• NEW BRAKES
• AUTO-LOCKING REAR DIFFERENTIAL
• TRAILER BRAKE CONTROLLER, INTEGRATED

Designed with your convenience in mind, this Silverado 1500 Custom offers a host of advanced technologies, including the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 System, Wireless Phone Projection, and a 120-Volt Bed Mounted Power Outlet. Stay connected and in control, whether you're navigating the city streets or tackling the open road.

Comfort and capability go hand-in-hand in this exceptional vehicle. The power driver's seat, power front and rear windows, and remote keyless entry ensure a comfortable and effortless driving experience. Plus, the integrated trailer brake controller and auto-locking rear differential make towing and hauling a breeze.

Safety is also a top priority in this Silverado. With features like Automatic Emergency Braking, Forward Collision Alert, and Lane Keep Assist with Lane Departure Warning, you can drive with confidence, knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

With its impressive fuel efficiency, delivering 18 MPG in the city and 21 MPG on the highway, this Silverado 1500 Custom is both practical and environmentally conscious. It's the perfect blend of power, technology, and efficiency.

This exceptional 2023 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 Custom is waiting for you to take it home. With its impressive features, sleek design, and uncompromising performance, it's the ultimate choice for those who demand the best. Visit our showroom today and experience the difference for yourself.

description:
Elevate every drive with this One-Owner 2019 Porsche Macan AWD, finished in sleek Black and engineered to deliver the perfect blend of athletic performance, refined luxury, and unmistakable Porsche presence. Powered by a responsive 2.0L Turbocharged engine paired with the quick-shifting 7-Speed PDK transmission, this Macan delivers thrilling acceleration, confident handling, and the everyday versatility that has made it one of Porsches most celebrated models.

Step inside and experience a cabin designed around premium comfort and precision. The 14-Way Power Seats with Memory Package allow each driver to find their perfect position, while Front & Rear Heated Seats and Front Seat Ventilation ensure year-round comfort. The expansive Panoramic Roof System fills the interior with natural light, enhancing the upscale atmosphere. Advanced convenience features such as Porsche Entry & Drive, HomeLink Garage Door Transmitter, Illuminated Entry, and a Power Liftgate elevate every moment behind the wheel.

Technology and connectivity come together seamlessly with Apple CarPlay including Siri, an intuitive Navigation System, and the immersive BOSE Surround Sound System creating a driving environment that keeps you engaged, informed, and entertained. Climate is effortlessly controlled through Automatic Temperature Control and Front Dual-Zone A/C, designed to keep both driver and passengers perfectly comfortable.

Safety and driving confidence are reinforced by Lane Change Assist, ParkAssist Front & Rear, Rain Sensing Wipers, Automatically Dimming Interior & Exterior Mirrors, and the advanced Porsche Dynamic Light System Plus (PDLS+), which enhances visibility in all conditions. Completing its commanding exterior presence are Sport Tailpipes in Black and stunning 21 Sport Classic Wheels in Exterior Color, adding a bold yet sophisticated finishing touch.

Recently arrived and meticulously maintained, this 2019 Macan offers timeless Porsche craftsmanship, exhilarating turbocharged performance, and an impressive suite of luxury features making it the perfect companion for both spirited weekend drives and everyday adventures.

description:
Step into luxury redefined with this stunning 2019 INFINITI QX80 LUXE in elegant Black Obsidian. This premium SUV transforms every journey into an experience worth savoring, whether you're navigating city streets or embarking on cross-country adventures. The commanding presence of its sophisticated exterior design turns heads, while the refined Graphite interior welcomes you into a sanctuary of comfort and technology.

According to the CARFAX report, this vehicle comes with a clean history and has never been involved in any accidents. The vehicle's mileage has been verified by CARFAX, giving you complete confidence in its odometer reading. For added peace of mind, CARFAX shows no damage has ever been reported on this well-maintained vehicle.

Imagine starting each morning with your perfect driving position automatically restored through the memory settings for your seat, steering wheel, and mirrors. The heated steering wheel and front seats offer welcome warmth on chilly days, while the tri-zone climate control ensures everyone travels in their ideal temperature zone. The power liftgate makes loading groceries or sports equipment a breeze, especially when your hands are full.

Weekend getaways become extraordinary experiences with the QX80's thoughtful amenities. The ProASSIST package provides peace of mind with features like adaptive cruise control and lane departure warning, letting you focus on the journey ahead. The premium sound system fills the cabin with concert-quality audio, while the rear entertainment system keeps passengers entertained on long drives. With seating for up to seven, including sumptuous leather-appointed seats and a flexible third row, there's room for the whole family and then some.

The 22" aluminum wheels and running boards add both style and functionality, making this QX80 as capable as it is beautiful. The advanced safety features, including blind spot monitoring and rear collision intervention, work quietly in the background to protect your precious cargo. At night, the automatic LED headlights with high beam assist illuminate your path while the ambient interior lighting creates a sophisticated atmosphere.

Whether you're dropping kids at school, heading to an important client meeting, or packing up for a ski weekend, this QX80 adapts to your lifestyle with elegant ease. The power-folding mirrors and around-view monitor make parking in tight spaces effortless, while the navigation system guides you confidently to your destination. With its perfect blend of luxury, technology, and versatility, this QX80 LUXE isn't just a vehicle – it's your partner in creating lasting memories.

description:
2018 Lexus RX 450hL Premium – One Owner | No Accidents | Luxury Hybrid SUV

The 2018 Lexus RX 450hL Premium is a refined luxury midsize hybrid SUV that blends upscale comfort, advanced safety technology, and impressive fuel efficiency. As the long-wheelbase version of the RX lineup, the RX 450hL adds a factory third row, offering seating for up to seven passengers—ideal for families who want flexibility without sacrificing Lexus craftsmanship.

Power comes from a smooth and efficient 3.5L V6 hybrid powertrain with all-wheel drive, delivering confident performance for daily driving and road trips alike while maintaining excellent fuel economy. Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully designed with premium leather seating, genuine wood trim, and a spacious three-row layout that balances passenger comfort with cargo versatility.

This RX 450hL Premium is a CARFAX 1-Owner vehicle with no accidents reported and strong service history, reflecting careful ownership and long-term reliability. Lexus Safety System features enhance peace of mind with Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Keep Assist, Collision Warning, Blind Spot Monitoring with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and a Color Head-Up Display, making long drives more relaxed and controlled.

Premium highlights include:
• 12.3" Navigation System
• Premium audio system with 12 speakers & subwoofer
• Heated & ventilated front seats
• Premium heated wood steering wheel
• Power tilt & slide sunroof
• 20" high-gloss alloy wheels
• Touchless power rear liftgate
• Cold Area Package

With its combination of luxury materials, advanced hybrid technology, proven Lexus reliability, and documented clean history, the 2018 Lexus RX 450hL Premium stands out as an excellent choice for buyers seeking a sophisticated, family-friendly luxury SUV.

One owner. No accidents. Well serviced. Hybrid efficiency with Lexus peace of mind.

description: The 2018 Porsche Macan GTS is a high-performance compact luxury SUV that blends Porsche's renowned driving dynamics with everyday practicality and premium comfort. Beneath its sleek and sporty exterior, the Macan GTS is powered by a twin-turbocharged V6 engine that delivers exhilarating acceleration and responsive handling. Its aggressive styling is complemented by distinctive xenon headlights, which provide excellent visibility and a signature design touch. Porsche's meticulous attention to detail is evident inside the cabin, where high-quality leather seats offer both comfort and support, creating a refined atmosphere ideal for daily commutes or spirited weekend drives.----Equipped with modern convenience and safety features, the 2018 Macan GTS enhances the driving experience with a host of thoughtful technologies. The hands-free liftgate allows for easy loading and unloading of cargo, ideal for busy lifestyles. A backup camera provides added confidence when maneuvering in tight spaces, while the lane departure warning system helps maintain safe driving habits on the highway. Automatic climate control ensures a comfortable interior environment regardless of the weather outside, maintaining precise temperature settings for all occupants. With its combination of performance, luxury, and innovative features, the 2018 Porsche Macan GTS stands out as a compelling choice for those who seek a versatile SUV with the spirit of a true sports car.

description: Experience premium comfort and advanced technology in this 2018 GMC Yukon Denali, finished in a stylish Quicksilver Metallic exterior. This full-size SUV comes equipped with top-of-the-line features including Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Keep Assist, and a Head-Up Display, offering a safer and more intuitive driving experience. The spacious interior features luxurious leather seats with a Third Row Seat providing comfortable seating for up to eight passengers. For added entertainment on longer trips, the Rear Seat Blu-Ray Entertainment System keeps passengers engaged, while the built-in Wi-Fi Hotspot ensures connectivity wherever you go. Convenience is elevated with Power Retractable Assist Steps and a Power Tilt-Sliding Sunroof that adds both practicality and open-air enjoyment.----This Yukon Denali also includes the exclusive Denali Ultimate Package, Enhanced Security Package, and Open Road Package, combining advanced comfort and protection features into one premium offering. Ride on striking 22-inch 6-Spoke Chrome Multi-Featured Design Wheels paired with P285/45R22 All-Season Blackwall Tires for a bold and confident stance on the road. All-Weather Floor Liners help keep the interior clean, regardless of the conditions outside. Aluminum wheels in an ultra-bright finish further highlight its commanding presence. Compliant with Federal Emissions Requirements, this vehicle includes the front license plate bracket and features such as Adaptive Cruise Control for a more relaxed drive. Designed for discerning drivers who appreciate space, technology, and luxury, the 2018 GMC Yukon Denali is your ultimate companion for both everyday commuting and extended road adventures.

Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and comfort in this exceptional 2018 Toyota 4Runner SR5 Premium. With its robust 4.0L V6 engine, 4-wheel drive, and impressive off-road prowess, this SUV is ready to take on any adventure you have in mind.

Designed to impress, the 4Runner's striking Gray exterior and premium features create a commanding presence on the road. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that prioritizes both style and functionality. Enjoy the convenience of the Entune Premium Audio system with Navigation, as well as the added comfort of heated front seats and an auto-dimming rearview mirror.

Whether you're commuting to the office or embarking on a weekend getaway, this 4Runner is up for the task. Its spacious interior and versatile cargo area provide ample room for passengers and gear, while the 4-wheel drive system ensures you can tackle any terrain with confidence.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front and side impact airbags, brake assist, and a rearview camera to give you peace of mind on the road. The 4Runner's impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 20 mpg on the highway, further enhances its everyday practicality.

Discover the perfect balance of power, capability, and comfort in this exceptional 2018 Toyota 4Runner SR5 Premium. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our dealership today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this versatile and well-equipped SUV.

description:
Experience the Pinnacle of Luxury and Efficiency with the 2018 Lexus RX 450h

Elevate your driving experience with the 2018 Lexus RX 450h, a remarkable fusion of advanced technology, exceptional comfort, and uncompromising performance. This stunning SUV is designed to captivate the senses and redefine your expectations of what a luxury vehicle can be.

• 3500 lbs Tow Prep Package
• Accessory Package
• Luxury Package
• 12 Speakers
• Panoramic Moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Backup Monitor
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• 12.3" Navigation System w/Mark Levinson Audio
• Color Heads-Up Display
• Panoramic View Monitor w/Blind Spot Monitor

Powered by a 3.5L V6 DOHC VVT-i 24V engine and equipped with an eCVT and AWD system, the RX 450h delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, achieving an impressive 31 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway. This advanced hybrid powertrain not only provides exceptional performance but also reduces your environmental impact, making it the perfect choice for the eco-conscious driver.

Step inside the RX 450h and be enveloped in a world of unparalleled luxury and craftsmanship. Indulge in the comfort of heated front and rear seats, a heated steering wheel, and a panoramic moonroof that floods the cabin with natural light. The 12.3-inch navigation system with Mark Levinson audio and the color heads-up display keep you connected and informed, while the Panoramic View Monitor with Blind Spot Monitor enhances your awareness and confidence on the road.

This 2018 Lexus RX 450h is Certified Pre-Owned, ensuring you can enjoy the peace of mind that comes with a comprehensive vehicle inspection and warranty coverage. description: This 2018 Mercedes-Benz GLS 63 AMG is pure luxury fused with supercar-level performance. Finished in stunning Brilliant Blue Metallic, this clean Carfax, local trade SUV delivers the perfect balance of space, comfort, and adrenalinemaking it one of the most impressive full-size performance SUVs ever built.Powering this AMG beast is a handcrafted 5.5L Twin-Turbo V8, producing a jaw-dropping 577 horsepower and 561 lb-ft of torque. Paired with AMG Performance 4MATIC all-wheel drive and adaptive air suspension, this GLS rockets from 060 mph in around 4.5 seconds, all while seating up to seven passengers in total comfort. Despite its performance, it still delivers a respectable 13 MPG city / 18 MPG highway for a high-output V8 luxury SUV.Inside, the cabin is pure first-class. Youll find premium leather seating, heated and ventilated front seats, multi-contour massage seats, panoramic sunroof, navigation, blind spot monitoring, and a harman/kardon Logic 7 surround sound system. The AMG Night Styling Package, black DINAMICA headliner, ambient lighting, and power-folding third row elevate the experience even further.Technology highlights include Apple CarPlay, adaptive suspension, auto high-beams, power liftgate, rear camera, rain-sensing wipers, and full COMAND navigation system. This GLS 63 also features a DVD drive for rear passengers, making it perfect for family trips without sacrificing performance.This is not just an SUVits a luxury rocket ship that offers AMG performance, S-Class comfort, and full-size utility in one incredibly rare package.Covert Ford of Hutto | 512-759-1414We are just a short drive from these areas Austin 78758, Round Rock 78665,78664, Georgetown 78626,78628,78633, Pflugerville 78660, Killeen 76540,76542, Temple 76513, 76502,76504, Elgin 78621, Taylor 76574, Bartlett 76511, Thorndale 76577, Coupland 78615, Granger 76530, Thrall 76578, Liberty Hill 78642, Leander 78641,78646, Jarell 76537, 78626 Cedar Park 78613,78630 Please come out and be a part of the Covert family.

An incredible adventure awaits behind the wheel of our Accident Free, One Owner 2018 Land Rover Range Rover SuperCharged Long Wheelbase 4WD with the Signature Entertainment Package offered in eye-catching Fuji White. Powered by a SuperCharged 5.0 Liter V8 offering 518hp tied to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission for impressive performance. An air suspension, a suite of aides, and advanced Four Wheel Drive allow this luxurious SUV to take you nearly anywhere you please, all while it attains nearly 19mpg on the highway. Whether covered in mud or shining with a fresh coat of wax, our Land Rover attracts attention with its aerodynamic styling enhanced with a panoramic sunroof, LED lighting, and lightweight alloy wheels. Step inside our Range Rover SuperCharged LWB, feel the soft Windsor leather, appreciate the tastefully placed wood accents, and familiarize yourself with the many amenities which surround you. Heated power front/outboard rear seats, a heated multi-function steering wheel, soft-close doors, power rear side-window sunshades, three-zone automatic climate control, and a power liftgate pamper you so you arrive at every destination completely relaxed. You'll also find this Land Rover includes a full-color InControl Touch Pro infotainment system to keep you seamlessly connected to your digital world with navigation, Bluetooth®, a USB input, and concert-quality Meridian audio. A check out the twin-screen rear seat entertainment system. Land Rover helps keep you safe and secure with forward collision warning, blind-spot monitoring, lane departure warning, traffic sign recognition, driver-drowsiness monitoring, a backup camera, and rain-sensing wipers. description:
2018 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon 4x4 – CARFAX 1-Owner | Legendary Off-Road Capability | Land Rover Fresno

This 2018 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon 4x4 is the ultimate expression of trail-rated performance, iconic Jeep design, and everyday usability. Built for serious off-road enthusiasts, the Rubicon trim comes equipped with heavy-duty hardware while still delivering comfort and modern technology for daily driving.

Under the hood is a powerful 3.6L V6 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, providing strong acceleration, smooth shifting, and dependable performance on and off the road. The Rubicon’s advanced 4x4 system, front and rear locking differentials, electronic sway bar disconnect, and rock-ready suspension make it one of the most capable SUVs ever produced.

The exterior features classic Wrangler styling with removable doors and roof panels, giving you the freedom of open-air driving. Inside, the cabin offers durable yet refined materials, leather-trimmed seating, and intuitive controls designed to handle both rugged adventures and city commutes with ease.

Technology and safety features include a user-friendly infotainment system, steering wheel-mounted controls, rearview camera, stability and traction control, and advanced braking systems—ensuring confidence whether navigating trails or highways.

This CARFAX 1-Owner vehicle reflects careful ownership and pride of maintenance. It has been thoroughly inspected and is ready for its next owner to enjoy with confidence.

Available now at Land Rover Fresno, this 2018 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon 4x4 is the perfect choice for drivers seeking unmatched off-road capability, timeless Jeep character, and proven reliability.

    • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you.     • Wireless connectivity - Strike the cord. Wireless technology makes it easy to place calls without having to fumble with your phone. It integrates your device with the system inside your vehicle for hands-free access. Keep connected and keep your hands on the wheel with wireless connectivity.

description: *Earnhardt Toyota of Mesa is pleased to offer you this 1-Owner 2023 Toyota Highlander XLE FWD in Magnetic Gray Metallic with a Black SofTex® interior.*This well-equipped 2023 Toyota Highlander XLE delivers a smooth ride, modern technology, and excellent everyday versatility in Magnetic Gray Metallic paired with a refined Black SofTex® interior. With *46,604 miles*, this *1-Owner* Highlander offers strong value for drivers seeking a dependable midsize SUV with three-row seating and proven Toyota reliability. Power comes from the turbocharged *2.4L 4-cylinder engine* paired with an *8-speed automatic transmission* and front-wheel drive, providing confident acceleration, quiet operation, and impressive efficiency with an EPA-estimated *22 MPG city and 29 MPG highway*.The interior and exterior styling come together seamlessly with a thoughtfully designed cabin featuring SofTex®-trimmed seating, a power-adjustable driver seat, tri-zone automatic climate control, push-button start, a large touchscreen infotainment system with smartphone integration, fade-to-off interior lighting, and flexible seating that comfortably accommodates passengers while offering generous cargo space. The XLE trim strikes an ideal balance of comfort, technology, and practicality for daily driving or longer trips.Safety and driver-assistance features include Toyota Safety Sense with Pre-Collision System, Lane Tracing Assist, Evasion Assist, Driver Monitoring Alert, adaptive cruise control, a backup camera, electronic stability and traction control, multiple airbags, and tire pressure monitoring, all designed to support confidence behind the wheel.On the outside, the Highlander presents a clean, modern SUV profile with LED lighting, roof rails for added versatility, deep-tinted glass, and smooth body lines that reflect Toyota's contemporary design language. The Magnetic Gray Metallic exterior adds a sleek, upscale appearance that's easy to maintain.If you're looking for a well-appointed, fuel-efficient midsize SUV with modern safety technology and a strong ownership history, this 2023 Toyota Highlander XLE is an excellent choice. Visit us today to experience it for yourself.*Earnhardt Toyota**6136 E Auto Loop Ave, Mesa, AZ 85206**480-807-9700*

Elevate your driving experience with the stunning 2023 GMC Terrain Denali. This exceptional SUV is a true testament to style, performance, and cutting-edge technology, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

Boasting a striking Black Diamond Edition, this Terrain Denali comes equipped with a host of premium features that set it apart from the crowd. Highlights include a powerful 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a 9-Speed Automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive, delivering an impressive blend of power and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 24 city/28 highway MPG, this SUV offers the perfect balance of performance and fuel economy.

• Black Diamond Edition
• Comfort Package
• Denali Premium Package
• License Plate Front Mounting Package
• Preferred Equipment Group 5SA

Step inside the Terrain Denali and experience the epitome of luxury and convenience. The cabin is adorned with premium leather-appointed seating, featuring heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a panoramic Skyscape power sunroof that floods the interior with natural light. The advanced GMC Infotainment Audio System with Navigation and a premium 7-speaker Bose sound system ensure you'll enjoy every mile with crystal-clear audio.

Cutting-edge technology abounds, with features like Wireless Apple CarPlay, Wireless Android Auto, and a Heads-Up Display that puts vital information right in your line of sight. The Terrain Denali also boasts an array of advanced safety systems, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Departure Warning, and Automatic Parking Assist, providing you with peace of mind on the road.

Exterior styling is equally impressive, with a bold and distinctive Black Onyx color scheme, 19-inch After Midnight painted aluminum wheels, and a power liftgate that adds both form and function. The Terrain Denali's sleek and sophisticated design is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

description: *Earnhardt Toyota of Mesa is pleased to offer you this 1-Owner 2023 Toyota Highlander XSE AWD in Wind Chill Pearl with a Cockpit Red leather interior.*This bold and sporty 2023 Toyota Highlander XSE AWD delivers confident performance, aggressive styling, and everyday versatility in Wind Chill Pearl paired with a striking Cockpit Red leather interior. With *58,284 miles*, this *1-Owner* Highlander offers strong value for drivers seeking a midsize SUV that stands out while maintaining Toyota's reputation for long-term reliability. Power comes from the turbocharged *2.4L 4-cylinder engine* paired with an *8-speed automatic transmission* and all-wheel drive, providing smooth acceleration, confident traction, and an EPA-estimated *21 MPG city and 28 MPG highway*.The interior and exterior design flow together seamlessly with a sport-inspired cabin featuring leather-trimmed seating, a power-adjustable driver seat, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, push-button start, a digital multi-information display, and Toyota's multimedia system with smartphone integration for a connected driving experience. The XSE trim adds unique styling touches that enhance both comfort and visual appeal while offering flexible seating and cargo space for daily driving or weekend adventures.Safety and driver-assistance features include Toyota Safety Sense with Pre-Collision System, Lane Tracing Assist, Evasion Assist, Driver Monitoring Alert, adaptive cruise control, electronic stability and traction control, multiple airbags, and tire pressure monitoring to help support confidence behind the wheel.On the outside, the Highlander XSE presents a bold SUV profile with LED lighting, sport-styled design accents, deep-tinted glass, and sculpted body lines that reflect Toyota's modern design language. The Wind Chill Pearl exterior gives this Highlander a clean, upscale presence that turns heads wherever it goes.If you're looking for a sporty, well-equipped AWD SUV with strong performance, modern technology, and a single-owner history, this 2023 Toyota Highlander XSE is a great choice. Visit us today to see it in person and take it for a drive.*Earnhardt Toyota**6136 E Auto Loop Ave, Mesa, AZ 85206**480-807-9700*

description:
With an original MSRP of $70,895, this 2023 BMW X5 xDrive45e combines plug-in hybrid efficiency with premium luxury, advanced technology, and confident all-wheel-drive performance. Designed to deliver electric driving capability for short trips while retaining the power and versatility of a gas engine, the xDrive45e offers an exceptional balance of efficiency and driving enjoyment.

The exterior is complemented by 21-inch bi-color wheels, a $1,550 upgrade that enhances the SUVs athletic stance. Inside, the cabin is equipped with a head-up display, originally priced at $1,100, projecting key driving information directly into the drivers line of sight for added convenience and safety. Heated front seats provide comfort in cooler conditions, while BMWs Connected Package Pro enhances connectivity and digital functionality.

Advanced driver assistance and parking technology further elevate the experience. The Parking Assistance Package includes Surround View camera technology and Active Park Distance Control, offering exceptional visibility and confidence when maneuvering in tight spaces. Apple CarPlay allows seamless smartphone integration for navigation, communication, and entertainment, while a rearview camera supports low-speed parking and reversing. Combining plug-in hybrid efficiency, premium features, and BMWs signature driving dynamics, this 2023 BMW X5 xDrive45e stands out as an excellent choice for drivers seeking a luxury SUV with modern efficiency and versatility.

This 2023 Nissan Pathfinder Platinum is a remarkable SUV that offers unparalleled comfort, technology, and versatility. With its spacious interior, advanced features, and exceptional performance, this vehicle is the perfect choice for discerning buyers who demand the best.

Under the hood, this Pathfinder is powered by a robust V6 engine paired with a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission, delivering an impressive 20 city/27 highway MPG. The front-wheel-drive configuration provides a confident and responsive driving experience, while the independent suspension ensures a comfortable ride.

The Platinum trim level elevates the Pathfinder's luxury and technology. Enjoy the premium Bose audio system, NissanConnect navigation, and a host of advanced safety features, including a Heads-Up Display, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert. The power liftgate and heated, ventilated front seats add to the Pathfinder's practicality and comfort.

Whether you're embarking on family adventures, commuting in style, or simply seeking a versatile and well-appointed SUV, this 2023 Nissan Pathfinder Platinum is an exceptional choice. This 2023 INFINITI QX50 SPORT is a true standout in the luxury SUV segment. With its sleek, modern design and impressive list of premium features, this vehicle is the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology.

The Bose Premium Audio System and INFINITI InTouch Navigation system ensure you'll enjoy every journey, while the Climate Controlled Front Bucket Seats and Ventilated Front Seats keep you comfortable no matter the weather.

The QX50's impressive safety features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, and Electronic Stability Control, provide you and your loved ones with the utmost protection. With a sleek Gray exterior and a well-appointed interior, this 2023 INFINITI QX50 SPORT is a true head-turner. The Power Liftgate and Panoramic Roof further enhance the vehicle's versatility and style, making it the perfect choice for those who demand the best.

Whether you're commuting to the office, embarking on a family road trip, or simply enjoying the open road, this QX50 is sure to exceed your expectations. With a city fuel economy of 22 MPG and a highway rating of 28 MPG, you'll enjoy impressive efficiency without sacrificing performance.

This 2023 Chevrolet Suburban Premier 1LZ delivers full-size SUV luxury, power, and space in one of the most capable vehicles on the road. Finished in Summit White with a Jet Black interior, this CARFAX One-Owner Suburban is exceptionally well equipped and ideal for families, road trips, towing, or executive-level transportation. Under the hood is the proven 5.3L EcoTec3 V8 paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission, providing smooth power delivery and confident performance. Rear-wheel drive keeps the ride refined while maintaining strong towing capability. The Premier 1LZ package adds top-tier comfort, technology, and safety features, making this Suburban one of the most desirable trims available. Key highlights include heated and ventilated front seats, heated second-row seats, a heated steering wheel, power-folding third-row seating, and power-release second-row bucket seats. The interior is further enhanced with memory seating, a power tilt and telescoping steering column, premium carpeting, and bright door sill plates. Technology features include a large infotainment display, Bose 10-speaker surround sound system with CenterPoint, wireless charging, SiriusXM with 360L, navigation capability, universal home remote, and a hands-free rear power liftgate. Safety and driver-assist features include lane change alert with side blind zone alert, rear cross traffic alert, safety alert seat, LED daytime running lights, and automatic emergency braking systems. This Suburban has completed a 145-point inspection, ensuring it meets high standards for quality, reliability, and peace of mind. Full-size SUVs with this level of equipment, condition, and ownership history are in extremely high demand. Don ??t miss your opportunity to own this 2023 Chevrolet Suburban Premier. We proudly serve drivers throughout the Phoenix metro area, including Scottsdale, Sun City, Avondale, Glendale, Cave Creek, Mesa, and Tempe. Contact us today to schedule your test drive before it ??s gone.

Under the hood, the 3.8L V6 engine ensures a powerful yet smooth driving experience, while the 8-speed automatic transmission offers seamless gear shifts. With an original MSRP of $52,045, this 2023 BMW X3 offers a refined combination of luxury, performance, and advanced technology in a versatile compact SUV. Finished in Dark Graphite Metallic, the exterior is complemented by striking 21-inch premium wheels, originally priced at $1,550, which enhance the vehicles athletic stance and upscale appearance. The Premium Package, originally priced at $2,650, adds a host of comfort and convenience features designed to elevate the everyday driving experience.

Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully appointed with Comfort Access keyless entry, heated front seats, and a heated steering wheel for added comfort in colder conditions. A panoramic moonroof brings natural light into the interior, creating an open and inviting atmosphere for both driver and passengers. BMW Live Cockpit Professional serves as the digital hub, integrating navigation, GPS, vehicle information, and entertainment into a sleek, driver-focused display. Additional technology features include Apple CarPlay for seamless smartphone connectivity and a rearview camera to assist with parking and low-speed maneuvering. Combining premium design, intuitive technology, and everyday practicality, this 2023 BMW X3 is an excellent choice for drivers seeking luxury and versatility in a compact SUV.

With an original MSRP of $74,645, this 2023 Land Rover Velar R-Dynamic delivers a refined blend of modern luxury, confident performance, and distinctive British design. The exterior is enhanced by 19-inch 5-spoke satin dark grey wheels, giving the Velar a sleek and contemporary road presence that reflects its performance-inspired character.

Equipped with Adaptive Cruise Control with Steering Assist, originally priced at $1,350, this Velar offers enhanced driving confidence and reduced fatigue on longer journeys. The air suspension, originally priced at $1,200, provides a smooth, composed ride while allowing for adjustable ride height to suit varying driving conditions. Step into the world of the 2023 Toyota Highlander XSE, where elegance meets performance. This used 4D Sport Utility vehicle, dressed in a striking Celestial Silver Metallic, is crafted for those who value both style and substance. description: Rediscover the Road with the 2023 Volkswagen Atlas 3.6L V6 SEL Premium R-Line: Where Luxury Meets Performance in a Sophisticated Deep Black Finish Step into the 2023 Volkswagen Atlas 3.6L V6 SEL Premium R-Line and experience a world of refined luxury and advanced technology tailored for the discerning driver. This used SUV, with its striking Deep Black exterior, is designed for those who crave both style and substance. Its powerful 3.6L Vr6 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission ensures a smooth and responsive drive, while the all-wheel-drive system offers confidence in any weather. Safety is paramount, with features like Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Keeping Assist, and Front Collision Mitigation providing peace of mind on every journey. The interior is a sanctuary of comfort, boasting leather seats, a panoramic roof, and a heated steering wheel.       Safety and Security
      • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
      • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

description:
2023 Ford Bronco Big Bend | 4x4, G.O.A.T. Modes, Removable Top The Ultimate Gainesville Adventure Rig!

Used 2023 Ford Bronco Big Bend for sale in Gainesville, FL. Off-road icon featuring Terrain Management System, Remote Start, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, and Pre-Collision Assist. The perfect trail-ready SUV for UF students, outdoor enthusiasts heading to Ginnie Springs, and weekend explorers at San Felasco Hammock.

Vehicle Description: Iconic Capability for the North Florida Wild
The 2023 Ford Bronco Big Bend is built for those who don't just live in Gainesville but explore every inch of Alachua County. While other SUVs are content with the pavement of Archer Road, the Bronco is designed to thrive where the asphalt ends. With its retro-modern styling, signature round LED headlamps, and Carbonized Gray grille, it makes a bold statement whether parked at Butler Town Center or staged for a tailgate near The Swamp. This is the vehicle for the driver who wants the freedom to take the doors off and feel the breeze on a cruise down Millhopper Road.

Why the Big Bend is the "Varsity" Choice for the 352:

Goes Over Any Terrain (G.O.A.T. Modes): With the standard Terrain Management System, you can toggle between six modes (including Sand and Mud/Ruts). Its the ultimate peace of mind for navigating the sandy trails of Paynes Prairie or the slippery limestone ramps at Lake Santa Fe.

Open-Air Gator Freedom: The Broncos most famous featurethe removable soft top and doorsallows you to transform your commute into an outdoor experience. Its the perfect way to soak in the Florida sunshine on your way to Devils Millhopper or a sunset view at Sweetwater Wetlands Park.

description:
Experience the epitome of luxury and performance with this stunning 2023 Lexus RX 350. Boasting a sleek Mica exterior and a meticulously crafted interior, this SUV is the perfect blend of style and substance.

Key features include:
• Navigation System
• Cold Area Package
• 12 Speakers
• Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto
• Wireless Charger
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• 19" Alloy Wheels
• Rain Sensing Wipers

Powered by a robust 2.4L I4 PDI Turbocharged engine, the RX 350 delivers an exhilarating 275 horsepower, ensuring a thrilling driving experience. With an impressive 29 MPG on the highway, this SUV combines performance and efficiency, making it the ultimate companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

The RX 350's interior is a sanctuary of refined elegance. Sink into the plush NuLuxe-trimmed seats and enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic climate control, a 9.8" touchscreen display, and a premium 12-speaker audio system. The digital key feature adds an extra layer of security and convenience, while the power liftgate and ample cargo space make loading and unloading a breeze.

Safety is paramount in the RX 350, with advanced features like the Lexus Safety System+, which includes Pre-Collision System, Lane Tracing Assist, and Intelligent High Beams. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your loved ones are well-protected.

This exceptional 2023 Lexus RX 350 is now available at our dealership. Experience the epitome of luxury and performance for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover why the RX 350 is the ultimate choice for the discerning SUV buyer.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Lexus NX 350h Base, a remarkable hybrid SUV that seamlessly blends style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This stunning vehicle is a true testament to Lexus' commitment to crafting vehicles that exceed expectations.

Boasting an impressive array of features, the 2023 Lexus NX 350h Base is designed to elevate your driving experience. Key highlights include:

• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth
• Heated Seats
• LED Headlights
• Leather Seats
• Memory Seat
• Navigation System
• Sunroof/Moonroof

The NX 350h Base is powered by a 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine, delivering exceptional fuel efficiency with an EPA-estimated 41 MPG in the city and 37 MPG on the highway. The seamless eCVT and standard AWD system ensure a smooth and confident ride, no matter the conditions.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium NuLuxe upholstery, a 10-speaker sound system, and a state-of-the-art navigation system with wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The dual-zone automatic climate control and heated front seats provide unparalleled comfort, while the power driver's seat with memory function allows you to find your perfect driving position with ease.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the 2023 Lexus NX 350h Base delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Automatic High Beams, Blind Spot Monitoring, and the Safety Connect emergency communication system.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2023 Lexus NX 350h Base. This exceptional hybrid SUV combines style, performance, and technology in a package that is sure to impress. Visit our showroom today to schedule a test drive and discover the true essence of Lexus craftsmanship.

With an impressive fuel economy of 18 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway, this SUV strikes a perfect balance between power and efficiency.

The Enclave's spacious and well-appointed interior is designed to accommodate the needs of growing families. The Perforated Leather-Appointed Seat Trim and heated front seats provide exceptional comfort, while the Power Driver Lumbar Control Seat Adjuster and Power Passenger Lumbar Control Seat Adjuster ensure a personalized fit. The 7-Passenger Seating configuration offers ample room for passengers and cargo, making it the perfect companion for your family adventures.

Staying connected on the go is a breeze with the Buick Infotainment System, which features Wireless Apple CarPlay and Wireless Android Auto integration. The premium audio system and SiriusXM with 360L provide an immersive listening experience, while the Rear Window Wiper and Variably Intermittent Wipers ensure clear visibility in any weather.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the Enclave delivers with a suite of advanced driver-assistance features. The Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Occupant Sensing Airbag provide comprehensive protection, while the Electronic Stability Control and 4-Wheel Disc Brakes with ABS Brakes enhance the vehicle's handling and stopping power.

This 2023 Buick Enclave Essence is a remarkable SUV that blends style, comfort, and technology. With its exceptional features, impressive performance, and uncompromising safety, it's the perfect choice for discerning buyers who demand the very best. Visit Grieco Mazda of Delray Beach today to experience the Enclave for yourself and discover why it's the ideal vehicle for your family.

description: Make a bold statement with this stunning Majestic White 2023 INFINITI QX55 SENSORY. As the top tier trim level for this model, the SENSORY edition offers the highest level of luxury and technology available. This vehicle is a recent arrival and has been driven very lightly, with an odometer reading that is over 6,600 miles below the market average. It comes with a clean vehicle history, a single previous owner, and is in excellent condition with all original records, books, and keys included.Choosing an INFINITI Certified Pre-Owned vehicle means you are getting a car that has passed a strict 167 point inspection. You will enjoy the security of an unlimited mileage factory warranty and the convenience of a one year prepaid service visit. This certification process ensures that your QX55 looks and drives like a brand new car, giving you the premium experience you deserve without the brand new price tag.The interior of this SENSORY model is truly a masterpiece, featuring soft Semi-Aniline leather seats and genuine wood door panel inserts. To keep everyone comfortable, it is equipped with climate controlled front seats that heat and cool, as well as heated rear seats for your passengers. One of the standout features is the Heads-Up Display, which projects important driving information directly onto the windshield so you can keep your eyes on the road while navigating through Clearwater.Technology enthusiasts will love the immersive sound of the 16 speaker Bose Performance Series audio system. The cabin is also equipped with a power moonroof, a heated steering wheel, and tri-zone automatic climate control to ensure every person in the car is perfectly comfortable. For added convenience, the motion-activated power liftgate allows you to open the trunk with a simple kick gesture when your hands are full of groceries or gear.This All-Wheel Drive crossover coupe offers a smooth and powerful ride thanks to its innovative VC-Turbo engine. With high-end safety features like auto high beam headlights and rain sensing wipers, you can feel confident driving in any conditions. We invite you to visit us at INFINITI of Clearwater to see this beautiful Majestic White QX55 for yourself. It is the perfect vehicle for someone who wants to combine the utility of an SUV with the sleek style of a sport coupe.INFINITI of Clearwater's pre-owned department believes in upfront, transparent, internet based pricing. Unlike our competitors, we don't have ads for reconditioning, tint (that many times was already installed), all weather mats, pin stripes, the list can go on and on! No ads, just simple, transparent, low prices! Call 727-275-8456 for more details!

description: This sophisticated Mineral Black 2023 INFINITI QX60 LUXE is now available for sale in Clearwater, Florida. As a top tier family SUV, it offers a smooth and powerful driving experience thanks to its 3.5L V6 engine and a refined 9-speed automatic transmission. This vehicle is INFINITI Certified, meaning it has passed a rigorous 167-point inspection and comes with an incredible unlimited mileage factory warranty. With a clean CarFax and only one previous owner, this QX60 arrives with all original records, books, and keys.The interior of the QX60 LUXE is designed to be a mobile sanctuary. You will enjoy the premium feel of leather-appointed seating surfaces and the versatility of a reclining third row for your passengers. To handle the Florida weather, the front seats are climate-controlled, offering both heating and ventilation, while the heated steering wheel adds a touch of comfort on cooler mornings. A large power moonroof opens up the cabin to natural light, making every journey feel more open and spacious.Music and technology lovers will be thrilled by the Performance Audio Package included in this model. It features the Bose Performance Series 17-speaker sound system, delivering concert-like audio throughout the entire cabin. The INFINITI InTouch Navigation system is built right in to help you find your way, while features like the power liftgate and rain-sensing wipers make your daily errands effortless. Whether you are commuting or heading out on a road trip, the tri-zone automatic climate control keeps everyone at their preferred temperature.Safety is paramount in this QX60, which features auto high-beam headlights and anti-whiplash front head restraints. It also comes equipped with the Cargo Package, featuring a reversible cargo mat and a first aid kit for added preparedness. On the outside, the vehicle sits on sporty 20-inch machined aluminum alloy wheels that perfectly complement the deep Mineral Black paint. With its sleek lines and elegant trim, this SUV is as beautiful as it is functional.At INFINITI of Clearwater, we take pride in offering high-quality, certified vehicles that are ready for the road. This QX60 represents the perfect blend of modern luxury and long-term peace of mind. Our straightforward pricing ensures you get a great value without any hidden fees or surprises. Come see this beautiful SUV in person and experience the quality of a certified INFINITI for yourself. Call 727-275-8456 today to schedule your visit!INFINITI of Clearwater's pre-owned department believes in upfront, transparent, internet based pricing. Unlike our competitors, we don't have adds for reconditioning, tint (that many times was already installed), all weather mats, pin stripes, the list can go on and on! No adds, just simple, transparent, low prices! Call 727-275-8456 for more details!

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2023 Acura RDX A-Spec Package. Boasting a sleek black exterior and a powerful 2.0L 16V DOHC engine paired with a 10-speed automatic transmission, this RDX delivers an exhilarating performance that will leave you in complete control.

Highlighting the vehicle's premium features, this RDX A-Spec Package is equipped with:

• Navigation system: Acura Navigation System with 3D View
• 16 Speakers
• Premium audio system: Acura/ELS Studio 3D
• Automatic temperature control
• Power driver seat
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS)
• Rear Parking Camera
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional handling and responsiveness of this Acura RDX. The A-Spec Package adds a touch of sportiness with its unique styling cues, including 20-inch Shark Gray split 5-spoke wheels and a distinctive front grille.

Acura's Precision Certified program ensures this RDX has undergone a rigorous 182-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty coverage. Enjoy the peace of mind of a 24-month/100,000-mile limited warranty, an 84-month/100,000-mile powertrain warranty, and complimentary maintenance services. Additionally, you'll receive roadside assistance, a vehicle history report, and access to the AcuraLink and SiriusXM services.

This meticulously maintained RDX with only 28,826 miles is the perfect blend of performance, luxury, and technology. Experience the exceptional craftsmanship and attention to detail that sets Acura apart. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this RDX can elevate your driving experience.

description: Pricing excludes tax, tag, title and pre-delivery service fee of $999 and private tag agency fee of $24.40. *See below for details..Volvo Certified!..Carfax 1 Owner!..Wow this All Wheel Drive XC90 Plud-In Hybrid T8 Plus 7 Passenger includes a 2.0L455 HP Turbocharged Gas/Electric 4 Cylinder Engine..8 Speed Automatic Transmission..Blind Spot Information System with Steer Assist..Rear Cross Traffic Alert with Autobrake..Surround View Camera..Pilot Assist with Adaptive Cruise Control..Collision Avoidance featuring: Low & High Speed Collision Mitigation, Detects Vehicle/Pedestrian/Cyclist/Large Animal..Driver Alert Control..Run-off Road Protection & Run-off Road Mitigation..Lane Departure Warning & Lane Keeping Aid..Oncoming Mitigation by Braking..4-Zone Climate Control..Front/Rear Park Assist Sensors..Panoramic Sunroof..Graphical Head-Up Display..Google-Based Infotainment System with Google Maps, Assistant and Google Play Store..12.3" Digital Driver Display..9" Touchscreen..Apple CarPlay..Harman/Kardon Audio System..Satellite Radio and a USB Port..Hands-Free Power Tailgate..Power Adjustable, Heated Leather Seats with 7 Passenger Seating..Heated Rear Seats..Integrated Second-Row Child Booster Seat..21" Alloy Wheels..Bluetooth for Phone & Audio..LED Headlights..Roof Rails..All power equipment and much more..Call Our Sales Team at 941-924-1212 For A Complete Description or Custom Video of this Vehicle..Own the Volvo you've always wanted..IntelliChoice has ranked our Certified Pre-Owned program number one in the premium segment nine times in the last ten years. Probably because each Certified Pre-Owned Volvo has to meet the strictest criteria and is backed by our best-in-class warranty. In fact, it was named Best Premium Warranty in 2018. Each Certified Pre-owned Volvo has to pass a rigorous 130-point test, have less than 80,000 miles, and receive a clear Vehicle History Report. We repair or replace any needed components, carefully checking the exterior and powertrain. We even do a road test. 5 year / Unlimited mileage warranty. We've got you covered. The factory-backed warranty fully covers every part of your Certified Pre-Owned Volvo that is not specifically excluded, including the replacement or repair of thousands of components. We also include free roadside assistance and a zero deductible for all warranty visits. (See dealer for details.)..What the reviews say..Powerful plug-in powertrain, high-end interior environs. The Volvo XC90 Hybrid three-row luxury SUV is upscale, quick, and efficientand it comes wrapped in a handsome body with a gorgeous Scandinavian-modern interior. Hybrid-powered luxury three-row family SUVs are a growing niche, and the 2023 Volvo XC90 Hybrid has the goods. Among luxury hybrid rivals such as the two-row Porsche Cayenne Hybrid and the BMW X5 Hybrid, the Volvo is the most fuel-efficient option. Its 455-hp powertrain conjures brisk acceleration from a turbocharged four-cylinder and electric motor, all-wheel is standard across the lineup. With its onboard battery fully charged, the XC90 Hybrid offers up to 32 miles of electric-only driving, which should be enough for many drivers daily commute. A host of tech features come standard, including a comprehensive driver-assistance suite. Premium materials line the cabin and the cozy Scandinavian vibe inside adds to the feeling of luxury. USB charging ports, a Google-based infotainment system, and an available high-end stereo system are there to ensure everyone remains connected and entertained. The XC90 T8 makes use of a turbocharged 2.0-liter four-cylinder that works with a rear-axle-mounted electric motor and a 14.7-kWh battery to whip up 455 horsepower and 523 pound-feet of torque. As with all XC90s, the T8 PHEV is only available with an eight-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive. The last time we tested a plug-in hybrid T8 model, it shot to 60 mph in just 4.5 seconds at our test track.

description: Step into luxury with this stunning Grand Blue 2023 INFINITI QX60 LUXE. This SUV is the perfect blend of style and practicality, making it an ideal choice for families or anyone who enjoys a smooth, premium ride. Because it is a recent arrival with a clean vehicle history and only one previous owner, you can drive away with total confidence knowing this vehicle has been meticulously cared for. It comes complete with all original records, books, and keys.As an INFINITI Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this QX60 offers incredible peace of mind that you simply won't find with a standard used car. It has passed a rigorous 167 point inspection and comes with an unlimited mileage factory warranty. You also get the added bonus of roadside assistance and a prepaid service visit included with your purchase. We take the guesswork out of buying pre-owned so you can focus on the joy of the open road.The interior of this LUXE trim is designed to keep everyone comfortable regardless of the Florida heat. It features beautiful leather seating surfaces with climate controlled front seats that can both heat up and cool down. The cabin stays perfectly chilled with dual zone front air conditioning and dedicated rear air conditioning for your passengers. Plus, the power moonroof lets in plenty of natural light, giving the spacious three row cabin an even more open and airy feel.Technology and convenience are at the heart of this QX60. Navigation is built right in to help you find your way around Clearwater and beyond, while the power liftgate makes loading groceries or gear a breeze. Safety is also a top priority, featuring auto high beam headlights, rain sensing wipers, and a security system to keep you and your loved ones protected. Whether you are carpooling to school or heading out on a weekend road trip, the 3.5L V6 engine provides plenty of power for a smooth and quiet journey.At INFINITI of Clearwater, we want your car buying experience to be just as premium as the vehicle you are driving. This QX60 stands out with its sporty 20 inch aluminum alloy wheels and sleek design. We invite you to come see it in person and experience the luxury for yourself. Our team is ready to answer any questions you have and show you why this SUV is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.INFINITI of Clearwater's pre-owned department believes in upfront, transparent, internet based pricing. Unlike our competitors, we don't have ads for reconditioning, tint (that many times was already installed), all weather mats, pin stripes, the list can go on and on! No ads, just simple, transparent, low prices! Call 727-275-8456 for more details!

description: Pricing excludes tax, tag, title and pre-delivery service fee of $999 and private tag agency fee of $24.40. *See below for details..Only 18,993 Miles!..Volvo Certified!..Carfax 1 Owner!..Wow this All Wheel Drive, XC60 B5 Ultimate includes Blind Spot Information System with Steer Assist and Rear Cross Traffic Alert..Surround-View Camera System..Side Parking Sensors..IntelliSafe Assist..Front/Rear Park Assist Sensors..12.3" Progressive Digital Driver Display..Google Based Infotainment System..Google Assistant..Google Maps..Google Play..Harman/Kardon Audio System..Wireless Smartphone Charging..Front/Rear USB Ports..9" Touchscreen Infotainment System with Navigation Mode..Satellite Radio, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto Smartphone Integration, and Bluetooth Connectivity..Lane Keeping Assist..Road Departure Mitigation and Protection..Collision Avoidance/Mitigation with Bike/Pedestrian/Animal Detection..Driver Alert Control..Power Adjustable, Heated/Cooled Leather Seats..Head-Up Display..Panoramic Moonroof..Power Tailgate..4-Zone Climate Control..22" Alloy Wheels..LED Headlights..Roof Rails..Keyless Drive..Enhanced Interior Ambient Lighting..Crystal Gear Selector Knob..2.0L Turbocharged Mild Hybrid 4 Cylinder with 247 HP..8 Speed Automatic Transmission..All power equipment and much more...Call Our Sales Team at 941-924-1212 For A Complete Description or Custom Video of this Vehicle..Own the Volvo you've always wanted..IntelliChoice has ranked our Certified Pre-Owned program number one in the premium segment nine times in the last ten years. Probably because each Certified Pre-Owned Volvo has to meet the strictest criteria and is backed by our best-in-class warranty. In fact, it was named Best Premium Warranty in 2018. Each Certified Pre-owned Volvo has to pass a rigorous 130-point test, have less than 80,000 miles, and receive a clear Vehicle History Report. We repair or replace any needed components, carefully checking the exterior and powertrain. We even do a road test. 5 year / Unlimited mileage warranty. We've got you covered. The factory-backed warranty fully covers every part of your Certified Pre-Owned Volvo that is not specifically excluded, including the replacement or repair of thousands of components. We also include free roadside assistance and a zero deductible for all warranty visits. (See dealer for details.)..What the reviews say..Sleek Scandinavian styling, efficient four-cylinder engines, premium cabin ambiance. Volvo's unique take on luxury is in full effect in the upscale and handsomely appointed XC60 SUV. Elegant design and purposeful engineering combine in the 2023 Volvo XC60, and the result is a distinctive option in the luxury-SUV class. A trio of four-cylinder powertrains is offered, the 247-hp B5, the 295-hp B6, and the 455-hp T8 plug-in hybrid. All of are reasonably fuel-efficient and feel good from behind the wheel, with performance that ranges from perky to downright quick depending upon which powertrain you choose. Technology is prioritized too, Volvo includes popular driver-assistance and safety features standard. The XC60 takes corners well, feels tied to the road while cruising, and changes directions with confidence. With interior styling and rich materials that mirror more expensive Volvos, the XC60 is like having your kladdkaka and eating it, too. The quiet, comfortable cabin also provides adult-sized accommodations in both rows. Overall, the 2023 Volvo XC60 is an intriguing and stylish alternative to the established BMW X3 and Mercedes-Benz GLC. Since the XC60 is a Volvo, safety plays a big part. You get all of the expected advanced safety features as standard equipment, while excellent crash test scores provide further assurance. It's even been named a Top Safety Pick+ by the Insurance Institute for Highway Safety.

description: This beautiful White 2023 Mercedes-Benz GLA 35 AMG SUV is the perfect choice for anyone who wants a compact vehicle with high-performance energy. As an AMG model, it offers a more exciting drive and a sportier look than your average crossover. It has a Clean CARFAX and has been meticulously maintained, meaning it is ready for its next owner to take it home. With the 4MATIC all-wheel drive system, you can enjoy confident handling in all types of road conditions.The interior of this GLA 35 AMG SUV features premium MB-Tex and Microfiber upholstery that looks and feels incredible. You'll stay comfortable year-round with heated front sport seats and dual zone automatic temperature control. The cabin is filled with convenient touches like the KEYLESS GO Package and HANDS-FREE ACCESS, which lets you open the power liftgate even when your hands are full of groceries. It also features a memory seat system, so your favorite driving position is saved at the touch of a button.Technology is front and center in this GLA 35 AMG SUV. The Premium Package includes high-quality displays with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, making it simple to use your phone's navigation and music. You can also enjoy a free trial of SiriusXM Radio through the premium MBUX audio system. For night driving, the Exterior Lighting Package with Adaptive Highbeam Assist and LED headlamps provides excellent visibility, automatically adjusting to the road and traffic around you.Safety is a top priority in this Mercedes-Benz. The GLA 35 AMG SUV comes with a rearview parking camera and rain-sensing wipers to help you see clearly in any situation. It also features advanced emergency systems like Active Emergency Stop Assist and a child-seat-sensing airbag for extra protection. The auto-dimming and power-folding side mirrors make navigating tight spaces or driving at night much easier. Every detail is designed to keep you and your passengers safe on every journey.Because this is a Mercedes-Benz Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, it has passed a strict 165-point inspection to ensure it is in top shape. It comes with an unlimited mileage factory warranty and 24/7 roadside assistance for your peace of mind. This GLA 35 AMG SUV combines the utility of a small SUV with the heart of a performance car. Come see us and experience what makes this vehicle so special.Check Availability Now or Call 727-306-9453.727-306-9453 Our Mercedes-Benz Factory Certification program is a curation of the very best Pre-Owned Mercedes-Benz vehicles available. Each and every one has passed a rigorous, 162-point Factory inspection and been completely reconditioned inside and out. All services and maintenance are up to date, including tires, brakes, belts, hoses and all fluids. Comes with 24/7 Roadside Assistance, Trip-Interruption Coverage, CARFAX service records available.

description:
The Certified 2023 Honda Passport EX-L in Obsidian Blue Pearl is a dependable and versatile midsize SUV that blends rugged capability with everyday comfort and modern style. Its Obsidian Blue Pearl exterior color gives the Passport a deep, rich, and sophisticated look. The dark blue paint shimmers in the light, subtly highlighting the vehicles bold lines, muscular stance, and confident presence on the road. Whether sitting in a driveway or heading out on a weekend adventure, the Obsidian Blue Pearl finish makes this SUV feel both elegant and ready for exploration.

Because this Passport is Certified Pre-Owned (CPO), it has been thoroughly inspected and reconditioned to meet Hondas high standards of quality and reliability. Certification usually includes thorough multi-point inspections, reconditioning work, and an extended warranty, providing extra peace of mind that youre getting a vehicle thats been carefully evaluated and is ready for many miles of dependable service. This added assurance makes the Passport EX-L an especially appealing choice for buyers who want the confidence of a certified vehicle.

Under the hood, the 2023 Passport EX-L is powered by a smooth and capable V6 engine that delivers confident performance in a variety of driving situations. Whether youre navigating city streets, merging onto highways, or tackling backroads, the engine offers responsive power and a well-balanced driving feel. The suspension is tuned to provide a comfortable ride for both driver and passengers, absorbing bumps and rough patches with ease. The Passports performance is designed to be versatile, giving you comfort on long drives and enough strength for towing or hauling when needed.

Step inside the Passport EX-L, and youll find a well-appointed cabin that focuses on comfort and convenience. The interior is spacious, with plenty of room for both front and rear passengers to stretch out. The EX-L trim adds premium touches like leather-trimmed seating surfaces, heated front seats, and a power-adjustable drivers seat that help make daily driving and longer journeys more enjoyable. The supportive seats and thoughtful layout create a comfortable environment thats ideal for family trips, errands, or weekend getaways.

Technology is well integrated into the Passports interior. The infotainment system features a clear and responsive touchscreen display that supports Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, so you can seamlessly connect your smartphone for music, navigation, messaging, and calls. Bluetooth connectivity and multiple USB ports help keep devices connected and charged, while other convenience features help make each drive more connected and enjoyable.

Cargo space is another strong suit of the Passport. The rear cargo area offers plenty of room for luggage, groceries, sports gear, or camping equipment. When you need even more space, the rear seats fold down to expand the cargo area, providing extra flexibility for hauling larger items. This practical design makes the Passport a great choice for active lifestyles or anyone who needs room for gear and passengers alike.

Safety is an important part of the 2023 Honda Passport EX-L experience. Honda equips this SUV with a suite of advanced driver-assist features designed to help enhance confidence and awareness on the road. These systems support tasks like lane-keeping, adaptive cruise control, and automatic emergency braking, helping contribute to a safer and more relaxed driving experience.

Overall, the Certified 2023 Honda Passport EX-L in Obsidian Blue Pearl offers a balanced blend of bold style, capable performance, modern technology, and everyday practicality. Its attractive exterior color, comfortable interior, thoughtful features, and CPO assurance make it a great choice for drivers and families looking for a reliable and versatile SUV thats ready for lifes journeysnear and far.

description:
Bold design, three-row luxury, and advanced driver technology define this 2023 Kia Telluride SX-Prestige AWD, a premium midsize SUV engineered to deliver comfort, confidence, and capability for families and professionals alike. With 31,112 miles and backed by Ford’s Blue Certified program, this Telluride offers added peace of mind through a comprehensive 139-point inspection, a 90-day/4,000-mile Comprehensive Limited Warranty, 24/7 Roadside Assistance, and fresh maintenance at delivery. Finished in Gravity Gray with a refined Black interior featuring premium Nappa leather seating, this SUV presents a sophisticated, commanding presence across Wesley Chapel, Tampa, Brandon, Clearwater, and St. Petersburg.

Power comes from Kia’s proven 3.8L GDI DOHC V6 engine paired with a smooth 8-speed automatic transmission. This powertrain delivers confident acceleration, strong highway passing performance, and refined cruising manners. The advanced all-wheel-drive system enhances traction and stability on wet pavement, sand, or uneven surfaces, making this Telluride well suited for Florida weather conditions and road trips alike. Trailer sway control and factory towing equipment add confidence when hauling recreational gear or small trailers.

The SX-Prestige trim represents the pinnacle of the Telluride lineup, blending luxury materials with cutting-edge technology. Inside the cabin, you’ll find heated and ventilated front bucket seats with memory, heated second-row seating, a heated leather-wrapped steering wheel, power-adjustable front seats with lumbar support, and upscale interior accents throughout. The three-row layout offers generous legroom for passengers in all rows, while the power-folding third row allows quick transitions between passenger seating and expanded cargo space.

Technology is a standout feature. Dual panoramic digital displays combine a fully digital instrument cluster with a large touchscreen infotainment system supporting Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth connectivity, voice recognition, and navigation functionality. The premium 10-speaker audio system delivers rich, immersive sound, while a head-up display projects key driving information directly into the driver’s line of sight. Multiple USB ports and power outlets throughout the cabin support modern device needs for every passenger.

Safety and driver-assist technology are extensive and confidence-inspiring. This Telluride includes Highway Driving Assist 2, Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop-and-Go, Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist with junction crossing detection, Blind Spot Monitoring with camera view, Rear Cross-Traffic Collision Avoidance, Lane Keeping Assist, Lane Following Assist, Driver Attention Warning, Parking Distance Warning with front and rear sensors, and a surround-view camera system. These systems work together to reduce driver stress and enhance awareness in both highway and city driving.

Exterior details reinforce the SX-Prestige’s upscale presence. Features include LED projector headlamps with automatic high beams, LED fog lamps, LED brakelights, power-folding heated mirrors with turn signal indicators, deep-tinted glass, chrome exterior accents, roof rails, a hands-free power liftgate, and distinctive 20-inch black-finish alloy wheels. The bold front grille and sculpted body lines give the Telluride a refined yet rugged appearance.

Ride quality is smooth, quiet, and composed. The Telluride absorbs road imperfections with ease while maintaining excellent highway stability and responsive steering. The elevated driving position provides outstanding visibility, and the well-insulated cabin creates a calm, comfortable environment for daily commutes or long-distance travel.

With a list price of $33,692, this SUV represents outstanding value in the full-size segment. Discover the confidence and capability that the Tahoe LS can bring to your daily drives and weekend adventures.

At our dealership, we're committed to providing you with a stress-free and enjoyable shopping experience. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and to help you find the perfect Tahoe to meet your needs. We invite you to schedule a test drive and experience the remarkable capabilities of this impressive SUV for yourself.

Don't miss the opportunity to own this well-equipped 2023 Chevrolet Tahoe LS. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

Discover the ultimate off-road companion in the 2023 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon 4xe. This exceptional vehicle combines the legendary Wrangler capabilities with the efficiency of a plug-in hybrid powertrain, making it the perfect choice for the adventurous driver seeking both performance and sustainability.

Boasting a host of premium features, this Wrangler Rubicon 4xe is equipped to tackle any terrain with ease. Key highlights include:

• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Automatic Emergency Braking
• Backup Camera
• Bluetooth
• Black 3-Piece Hard Top
• Trailer Tow & Aux Switch Group
• Quick Order Package 29V Rubicon
• Navigation System
• 9 Speakers
• Rear Window Defroster
• Power Steering
• Power Windows

• Auxiliary Switches
• Front Bucket Seats

With its 4WD capability and exceptional off-road features, this Rubicon 4xe is ready to conquer any adventure, whether it's scaling rugged trails or navigating the urban jungle.

Imagine the thrill of driving this Jeep Wrangler Rubicon 4xe, with its unparalleled combination of capability, technology, and sustainability. Experience the freedom and versatility that only a true Wrangler can provide, now with the added benefits of electrified performance.

We invite you to visit our showroom and take this remarkable Wrangler Rubicon 4xe for a test drive. Discover the confidence and excitement that come with owning this exceptional vehicle. Let us demonstrate how it can transform your driving experience and elevate your adventures to new heights.

Contact us today to schedule your personal test drive and unlock the full potential of the 2023 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon 4xe.

PRESTIGE PACKAGE, BLACK, LEATHER SEATING SURFACES, BLACK OPTIC SPORT PACKAGE Convenience
  • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Audi smartphone interface (Apple CarPlay/Android Auto) smart device wireless mirroring
Automatic Full-Time All-Wheel, Express Open/Close Sliding And Tilting Glass Panoramic 1st And 2nd Row Sunroof w/Power Sunshade, Perimeter/Approach Lights, 8-Way Power Driver Seat -inc: Power Recline, Height Adjustment, Fore/Aft Movement and Cushion Tilt, 8-Way Power Passenger Seat -inc: Power Recline, Height Adjustment, Fore/Aft Movement and Cushion Tilt, Heated/Cooled Front Cupholder, Perimeter Alarm, 3 12V DC Power Outlets, Audi side assist Blind Spot, Audi pre sense city, Audi Pre Sense Rear, Collision Mitigation-Front To be sure you don't miss out, give us a call at (888) 685-1813 and schedule a test drive. Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2023 GMC Acadia Denali. This stunning SUV boasts a captivating White Frost Tricoat exterior, complemented by a wealth of premium features that will redefine your expectations.

Highlighted by:
- Fully Serviced and Detailed
- Denali Technology Package
- Trailering Package
- Dual SkyScape 2-Panel Power Sunroof
- Bose Premium 8-Speaker Audio System
- Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto
- Heated & Ventilated Driver & Front Passenger Seats
- Rear Camera Mirror Washer
- Hitch Guidance w/Hitch View
- Trailering Assist Guidelines

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 SIDI engine and equipped with an advanced 9-speed automatic transmission, this Acadia Denali delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with an estimated 19 city/26 highway MPG. The available all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling and exceptional traction, making this SUV a versatile companion for any journey.

Step inside and experience the epitome of luxury and technology. The Denali Technology Package, featuring HD Surround Vision, Adaptive Cruise Control, Enhanced Automatic Emergency Braking, and the Rear Camera Mirror, elevates your driving experience to new heights. The dual-panel power sunroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere.

Indulge in the comfort of the Denali's premium leather-appointed seating, with heated and ventilated front seats and heated rear outboard seats. The driver and front passenger can enjoy the convenience of power lumbar controls, while the memory seating feature allows you to personalize your perfect driving position.

Connectivity is seamless with the 8-inch diagonal multi-touch navigation system, which integrates with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The Bose premium audio system ensures your music is delivered with exceptional clarity and depth, enhancing every drive.

For those with an active lifestyle, the Trailering Package equips this Acadia Denali with a factory-installed hitch, 4,000-pound towing capacity, and a heavy-duty cooling system, making it the ideal companion for your adventures.

This exceptional 2023 GMC Acadia Denali is a true testament to the brand's commitment to excellence. Experience the pinnacle of luxury, technology, and capability in this remarkable SUV. Visit our showroom today to explore this remarkable vehicle and discover how it can elevate your driving experience.
