description:
Elevate your driving experience with this meticulously maintained 2023 Ford Explorer XLT. This exceptional SUV boasts a stylish gray exterior and a well-appointed interior, ready to take you on your next adventure.

Highlights of this Explorer XLT include:

• Front & Second Row Floor Liners
• Daytime Running Lamps (DRL)
• Equipment Group 200A

The 2.3L EcoBoost I-4 engine, paired with a 10-Speed Automatic transmission and Rear-Wheel Drive, delivers an impressive blend of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 21 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway.

This Explorer XLT is packed with a wealth of premium features that prioritize your comfort and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of the SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a power liftgate. The heated front seats and leather-wrapped steering wheel add a touch of luxury, while the four-wheel independent suspension and speed-sensing steering ensure a smooth and responsive ride.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, electronic stability control, and a rearview camera to give you peace of mind on the road.

As a Ford Gold Certified pre-owned vehicle, this Explorer XLT has undergone a rigorous 172-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty package. Enjoy the reassurance of 12 months/12,000 miles of limited warranty coverage, an 84-month/100,000-mile powertrain warranty, and 22,000 FordPass Rewards Points to use toward your first two maintenance visits.

Don't miss the opportunity to experience the exceptional quality and value of this 2023 Ford Explorer XLT. Schedule a test drive today and discover the perfect blend of performance, comfort, and peace of mind.

Discover the Unparalleled Luxury of the 2023 Cadillac XT4 Luxury

The 2023 Cadillac XT4 Luxury is a true masterpiece of automotive engineering, blending sophisticated style, advanced technology, and uncompromising performance. This exceptional SUV is the embodiment of Cadillac's commitment to delivering a driving experience that is truly extraordinary.

Key features of this remarkable vehicle include:

• Local Trade
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• One Owner
• Wi-Fi Hotspot
• Sunroof, Power, Dual Panel Glass, Tilt/Sliding
• Cadillac User Experience with Embedded Navigation
• Bose Centerpoint Surround Sound 13-Speaker Audio System
• Leather Seating Surfaces
• Cold Weather Package with Heated Seats and Steering Wheel

Beneath the stunning exterior lies a powerful 2.0L I4 Turbocharged engine, mated to a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission and Cadillac's renowned All-Wheel Drive system. This powertrain delivers an exceptional balance of efficiency and responsiveness, with an impressive EPA-estimated 22 city/29 highway MPG.

The Cadillac XT4 Luxury is more than just a vehicle – it's a statement of refined taste and uncompromising standards. The interior is a masterclass in luxury, with premium materials, meticulously crafted details, and an array of advanced technologies that seamlessly integrate with your connected lifestyle.

From the moment you slide behind the wheel, you'll be captivated by the XT4's responsive handling and confident road presence. The available Cold Weather Package ensures you can enjoy this exceptional SUV in any season, with heated seats and a heated steering wheel to keep you comfortable and in control.

Whether you're commuting in style, embarking on a weekend adventure, or simply seeking a vehicle that reflects your discerning taste, the 2023 Cadillac XT4 Luxury is the perfect choice. Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance – schedule a test drive today and discover why the XT4 is the SUV that truly sets the standard.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2023 INFINITI QX80 LUXE. This stunning SUV offers a captivating blend of power, sophistication, and cutting-edge technology, making it the perfect companion for your adventures.

Boasting a powerful 5.6L V8 engine and 4-wheel drive, the QX80 LUXE delivers an impressive performance that will leave you in awe. The power-adjustable driver's seat with memory function allows you to find your perfect driving position, while the Rear Air Conditioning and Rear Window Defroster keep everyone comfortable.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the QX80 LUXE delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. Enjoy the peace of mind of Intelligent Cruise Control, Automatic Emergency Braking, and Blind Spot Monitoring, among other cutting-edge technologies.

This exceptional 2023 INFINITI QX80 LUXE is a true testament to the brand's commitment to excellence. With its uncompromising performance, refined luxury, and innovative technology, it's the perfect choice for those who demand the best. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance with this exceptional 2023 BMW X1 xDrive28i. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this dynamic SUV combines the best of BMW's engineering prowess and innovative technology, creating a driving experience that is both thrilling and refined.

Boasting a robust 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V TwinPower Turbo engine paired with a smooth 7-Speed Automatic transmission, this X1 delivers impressive power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 city/34 highway MPG. The intelligent xDrive all-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling, even in challenging road conditions.

This particular X1 comes equipped with a remarkable array of premium features, including:
• Local Trade
• Apple Car Play/Android Auto
• One Owner
• Wi-Fi Hotspot
• Wireless Device Charging
• Premium Sound System
• Head-Up Display
• Panoramic Moonroof
• Parking Assistant Plus
• Heated Front Seats and Steering Wheel
• Remote Engine Start

The PREMIUM PACKAGE takes this X1 to the next level, offering an exceptional array of advanced technologies and luxurious amenities. Enjoy the convenience of Comfort Access Keyless Entry, the clarity of the harman/kardon® Premium Sound System, and the added safety and awareness of the Surround View with 3D View and the intuitive Head-Up Display.

Elevate your driving experience with the xLine Design, which adds distinctive styling cues and premium materials throughout the cabin, including the Sensatec Dashboard and Sport Seats. The 19-inch Y Spoke Bi-Color wheels further enhance the X1's dynamic presence.

Whether you're commuting in the city, embarking on a weekend getaway, or tackling your daily adventures, this 2023 BMW X1 xDrive28i is the perfect companion. Its blend of power, efficiency, and cutting-edge technology, combined with the renowned BMW driving dynamics, make it a truly exceptional choice.

We invite you to experience the exceptional craftsmanship and performance of this 2023 BMW X1 xDrive28i for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable SUV can elevate your driving experience. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be captivated by its unparalleled capabilities and luxurious refinement.

The rear seats fold easily to expand the cargo area further, adding versatility for weekend trips or larger loads. In summary, this 2023 Lincoln Nautilus AWD Reserve with 26,220 miles, a clean CarFax report, and one owner combines premium comfort, modern technology, and confident all-wheel drive performance. Its excellent condition and thoughtful features make it an attractive option for anyone seeking a luxury SUV with everyday usability and refined style.

description:
When you need a high-quality luxury SUV at a competitive price, the used inventory at Autobahn Volvo in Fort Worth delivers exceptional value, premium features, and peace of mind-and this Certified 2023 Volvo XC60 B5 Plus Bright Theme AWD is a perfect example. Finished in striking Onyx Black Metallic, this recently arrived XC60 blends Scandinavian design, advanced safety, and confident all-wheel-drive performance into one refined package. With an original MSRP of $54,840, an odometer reading of just 21,147 miles, and mileage 13,922 miles below the market average, this SUV represents an outstanding opportunity for drivers near Fort Worth, Weatherford, Burleson, Flower Mound, and Arlington, TX.

Under the hood, the XC60 B5 is powered by a 2.0L I4 Turbocharged engine paired with a smooth Automatic with Geartronic transmission, delivering responsive acceleration, impressive efficiency, and confident traction thanks to Volvo's AWD system. EPA-estimated 23 MPG city/29 MPG highway makes this luxury SUV practical for both daily commutes and long road trips, while Volvo's refined ride quality ensures comfort at every mile.

This Plus Bright Theme model is equipped with a highly desirable list of high-value features designed to enhance comfort, convenience, and protection. Highlights include the Climate Package with Heated Rear Seats and a Heated Steering Wheel, perfect for cooler mornings and winter drives. The 20" 5-Multi Spoke Black Diamond Cut Alloy Wheels add a bold, upscale appearance, while the Protection Package Premier includes a Bumper Cover, Cargo Tray, Rubber Floor Mats, and Wheel Locks to help preserve the vehicle's condition. Additional thoughtful touches such as a First Aid Kit further reflect Volvo's commitment to safety and preparedness.

As a Certified by Volvo vehicle, this XC60 has passed a rigorous 170+ point inspection, ensuring it meets Volvo's exacting standards for quality and performance. Certification also provides exceptional ownership benefits, including a 12-month/unlimited-mile Certified Limited Warranty, which is upgradeable up to 5 years and unlimited miles, with a $0 deductible. You'll also enjoy 24/7 Roadside Assistance, a transferable warranty, and a Vehicle History Report with Buyback Guarantee for added confidence. Included is 1 year of complimentary Volvo On Call, giving you access to remote start, climate control, door locks, vehicle location, maintenance reminders, and a digital driving journal right from your smartphone.

This XC60 is located at our Volvo Store and is ready for immediate delivery. Autobahn Volvo proudly uses market-based pricing, so you can be confident this vehicle is priced competitively within current market conditions. With our wide selection of Certified Pre-Owned Volvo models, finding a luxury vehicle you'll love at a price you can feel good about is easy.

To make your shopping experience even more convenient, we offer virtual walkarounds-just ask your sales associate to see this XC60 up close from the comfort of your own home. For more information or to schedule your personalized walkaround, call us today at (817) 390-3236. Discover why so many drivers choose Autobahn Volvo in Fort Worth for quality vehicles, transparent pricing, and exceptional customer care.

Introducing the 2023 Toyota Highlander L, a captivating SUV that seamlessly blends style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This exceptional vehicle is priced below market value, making it an irresistible choice for discerning buyers seeking unparalleled value and a driving experience that exceeds expectations.

The 2023 Toyota Highlander L boasts a powerful 2.4L I4 PDI Turbocharged DOHC 16V LEV3-SULEV30 265hp engine, mated to an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, delivering an exceptional blend of power and efficiency. With an impressive EPA-estimated 22 city/29 highway MPG, this SUV ensures you can conquer the open road with confidence and style.

Stepping inside the 2023 Highlander L, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, designed to cater to your every need. The split-bench third-row seating offers versatility, allowing you to accommodate your family and friends with ease. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, seamlessly integrating your smartphone with the vehicle's advanced infotainment system.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the 2023 Highlander L delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear provides added peace of mind when maneuvering in tight spaces, while the Emergency Communication System with Safety Connect ensures you're connected to emergency services in the event of an incident.

Experience the unparalleled comfort and refinement of the 2023 Toyota Highlander L. This exceptional SUV is a true testament to Toyota's commitment to quality, reliability, and customer satisfaction. Visit us at Hiley Hyundai/Mazda of Burleson to schedule a test drive and discover the joy of owning this remarkable vehicle.

Don't let this opportunity slip away. The 2023 Toyota Highlander L is sure to captivate and impress. Contact us today at (817) 241-2516 to secure your chance to own this remarkable SUV.

description:
Unlock the Rugged Adventure of the 2023 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon

Elevate your off-road experience with the exceptional 2023 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon, now available at our dealership. This iconic SUV combines unparalleled capability, advanced technology, and refined style, making it the ultimate companion for your next outdoor excursion.

Boasting a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, the Wrangler Rubicon delivers impressive power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/24 highway MPG. Equipped with legendary 4WD, this Jeep is ready to conquer any terrain, from the winding backroads to the most challenging off-road trails.

Elevate your driving experience with the following premium features:
• Navigation System
• ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera
• 9 Speakers
• Radio: Uconnect 4C Nav w/8.4" Display
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Performance Suspension
• Blind Spot & Cross Path Detection
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Heated Front Seats
• Leather Trimmed Bucket Seats

Designed to take on the toughest challenges, the Wrangler Rubicon boasts a Trailer Tow & Aux Switch Group, including a Class II Receiver Hitch and 7 & 4 Pin Wiring Harness, making it the perfect companion for your outdoor adventures. The Jeep Trail Rated Kit and Body Color Rubicon Highline Flare add a touch of rugged style, while the MOPAR All-Weather Floor Mats ensure your Wrangler stays pristine, no matter the conditions.

Discover the ultimate blend of capability, technology, and style with the 2023 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon. Visit our showroom today and experience the thrill of off-road dominance for yourself. We're confident this Wrangler will exceed your expectations and become the perfect partner for your next journey.

Step inside and be enveloped in a world of luxury and convenience. The advanced SYNC 4 infotainment system, complete with built-in Alexa, seamlessly integrates your digital life, while the 360-degree camera and advanced driver-assist technologies provide unparalleled confidence and control.

This Nautilus Reserve is also backed by Lincoln's Certified Pre-Owned program, ensuring you can purchase with confidence. Each Certified Pre-Owned Lincoln undergoes a rigorous 200-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty, providing you with the peace of mind you deserve.

Experience the epitome of luxury and performance in the 2023 Lincoln Nautilus Reserve. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional SUV can elevate your driving experience.

description: Canyon State Classics brings to market a super clean Mercedes-Benz G500. This beautiful has always been dealer serviced as evidenced by its pages long Carfax and Mercedes Internal VMI service history print-off which is included with the vehicle offered here. The truck had an original MSRP in 2004 of over $80,000, so dont miss your chance to own this beauty for a fraction of the original sticker. The following is a list of options as this G500 is currently equipped: -5.0L V8 with 292hp -4Matic Four Wheel Drive w/ 3 Locking Diffs -5 Speed Automatic -Upgraded 20 G55 Wheels w/ Pirelli All Season Tires -Full Leather Interior -Full Burl Walnut Accent Kit -Heated Power Front Seats -Heated Rear Seats -Dual Zone Climate Control -Rear Air Conditioning -Backup Sensors and Camera -Auto Dimming Mirrors -Premium Bose Sound with 6 CD Changer MP3 Capable -GPS Navigation System -Power Adjustable Heated Steering Wheel The body on this G500 is in excellent condition overall. The car is finished in Gloss Black, which is an absolutely gorgeous color and people will take notice when you pull up. The paint on the car has been garage kept and is overall very nice and looks great with only a few blemishes on a few parts of the SUV which are pictured. The truck is super straight and has never had any paint work or accident damage. The truck just received an upgraded wheel package G55 20 alloys. The interior is in great shape all around. The Black Nappa leather interior and walnut trim is all very nice and doesnt show any ware at all. All seats, door panels, carpets, and floor mats are in very good condition and look like new. The interior is extremely comfortable and well optioned. All accessories work inside the car including the heated seats, Navi, CD Player, sound system, etc. The car has never been smoked in and has a fresh smell of fine woods and leathers. Overall condition of the interior is a 9 out of 10. Mechanically, this G500 runs like a top. I cant describe how nice this car drives. It is extremely smooth and luxurious, but with the stomp of your foot you unleash all the power of the V8. The motor provides ample power to move the car around. All correct accessories are in place and the motor has been completely cleaned and detailed to original condition. This car has a documented extensive dealer service history since day one which will be included with the car. I have all dealer print-offs of warrantee work as well as customer pay information. The G is tight as a drum with no leaks and just had thousands in major servicing completed. If you have been searching for a very nice G500 in the best color combo, the search ends here. If you have any additional questions please call Jon at 480-703-2337.

description:
Welcome to Hyundai of Yakima, this used 2026 Hyundai Kona Limited with only 896 miles is a standout choice for drivers in Yakima and Central Washington who want the right vehicle at the right price. At Hyundai of Yakima, we select vehicles that deliver real value, dependability, and everyday confidence. Hyundai of Yakima is the #1 source for buying pre-owned vehicles in Central Washington. Every used vehicle at Hyundai of Yakima goes through a thorough 152+ point inspection to ensure safety, performance, and peace of mind. Inventory is moving fast, let us help maximize your tax refund to help lower your monthly payments or lower the overall price of your next vehicle. This vehicle is a No Accidents! One Owner! This Vehicle is Equipped with: Convenience
  • GPS linked cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until GPS linked cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed and the system uses GPS navigation data to maintain that speed without driver intervention - including slowing down for curves and anticipating hills. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Meet your ultimate co-pilot, GPS linked cruise control.
Safety and Security
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. description: DEALER SERVICED **, FULLY DETAILED **, FRESH OIL CHANGE **, 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V. 2026 Honda CR-V Hybrid Sport-L AWD eCVT 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V Odometer is 3515 miles below market average! 40/34 City/Highway MPG Crenshaw Hyundai is family owned and operated. The founder Charles Crenshaw, born in Kings Mountain and raised in Alamance county North Carolina and a sergeant in the Marine Corps, began his career in 1959 working for Atwater Ford in Burlington. He worked for the Atwaters until 1977, at that point he went into business for himself, starting a Datsun dealership in Sanford, NC. In the winter of 1982 he had the opportunity to return to his home in Burlington, NC and he and Terry Crenshaw have been operating Carolina Nissan since then. In the fall of 2005, after interviewing many candidates, Hyundai approached Mr.Crenshaw and the Crenshaw family to find out if they would be interested in opening a Hyundai franchise in Burlington. Crenshaw Hyundai opened in Jan. Of 2008. Mr. Crenshaw was awarded the Hyundai franchise because of his experience and leadership and customer satisfaction in their sales, service and parts departments and because of his commitment to: 'Put the Customer First!' Give us a call today 336.584.1144 or email us at info@crenshawhyundai.com for availability. Come visit in person us at Crenshaw Hyundai, 330 Huffman Mill Rd, Burlington, NC, 27215 or as always you can shop 24/7 at www.crenshawhyundai.net.

With only 4,501 miles on the odometer, this crossover is practically new and loaded with premium features. Safety is top-notch thanks to advanced systems like Intersection Cross Pre-collision Warning, Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keeping Assist, Adaptive Cruise Control, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and Blind Spot Safety. description:
Discover the Epitome of Versatility and Sophistication: The 2024 Kia Telluride EX X-Line

Elevate your driving experience with the captivating 2024 Kia Telluride EX X-Line. This exceptional SUV seamlessly blends power, style, and cutting-edge technology, making it the ultimate companion for your adventures.

Boasting a robust 3.8L V6 DOHC engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive, the Telluride EX X-Line delivers a thrilling performance that will leave you in awe. With an impressive 18 MPG in the city and 24 MPG on the highway, this SUV strikes the perfect balance between power and efficiency.

Indulge in the following premium features:
• Bluetooth
• Leather
• Heated seats
• Blind Spot Monitors
• Rear view camera
• Power Windows & Locks

The Telluride EX X-Line also offers a wealth of advanced technology, including a Navigation System, 6 Speakers, SiriusXM radio, and a premium AM/FM Display Audio System. Stay connected and entertained throughout your journey with seamless integration of your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto.

Elevate your comfort with the Telluride's exceptional climate control features, including Automatic temperature control, Front dual zone A/C, and Rear air conditioning. The Power driver seat, Heated & Ventilated Front Bucket Seats, and Leather Seat Trim ensure you and your passengers travel in unparalleled luxury.

Safety is paramount in the Telluride EX X-Line, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Enjoy the peace of mind of features like Dual front impact airbags, Dual front side impact airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and Rear side impact airbag.

Enhance your driving experience with the Telluride's impressive array of convenience features, including a Power Liftgate, Smart Key with Push Button and Remote Start, and a Panoramic Sunroof. Indulge in the convenience of the Heated steering wheel, Leather Shift Knob, and Telescoping steering wheel, all designed to make every drive a pleasure.

With its striking exterior, featuring Alloy wheels and a Rear window wiper, the Telluride EX X-Line commands attention wherever it goes. The Roof rack: rails only and Spoiler add a touch of sophistication and practicality to this remarkable SUV.

Discover the epitome of versatility and sophistication in the 2024 Kia Telluride EX X-Line. Experience the thrill of owning a vehicle that seamlessly blends power, technology, and luxury. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Telluride EX X-Line is the perfect choice for your next adventure.

description:
The 2024 Jaguar F-PACE P250 R-Dynamic S is a luxury compact SUV that combines sporty performance with elegant design and advanced technology. Here's an overview of its key features and specifications:
Performance & Drivetrain
- Engine: 2.0-liter turbocharged inline-4 engine
- Horsepower: 246 hp at 5,500 rpm
- Torque: 269 lb-ft at 1,300 rpm
- Transmission: 8-speed automatic
- Drivetrain: All-Wheel Drive (AWD)
- 0–60 mph: Approximately 6.9 seconds
- Top Speed: 135 mph
- Fuel Economy: 22 mpg city/27 mpg highway
- Towing Capacity: Up to 5,291 lbs

Dimensions & Capacity
- Length: 186.9 inches
- Width: 85.6 inches (with mirrors)
- Height: 65.5 inches
- Wheelbase: 113.1 inches
- Ground Clearance: 8.4 inches
- Curb Weight: 4,015 lbs
- Seating Capacity: 5 passengers
- Cargo Capacity: 32.1 cu ft (rear seats up)

Interior & Technology
- Infotainment System: Pivi Pro with 11.4-inch touchscreen
- Audio System: 12-speaker Meridian sound system
- Connectivity: Apple CarPlay and Android Auto (wireless)
- Charging: Wireless device charger
- Climate Control: Dual-zone automatic
- Seating: DuoLeather sport seats
- Steering Wheel: Heated, leather-wrapped
- Driver Assistance Features:
- Blind Spot Assist
- Lane Keep Assist
- Traffic Sign Recognition
- Active Cruise Control
- Rearview Camera
- Hill Launch Assist
- JaguarDrive Control

Exterior Features
- Wheels: 19-inch alloy wheels (standard), optional 20-inch wheels
- Lighting: LED headlights with signature daytime running lights
- Mirrors: Heated, power-folding exterior mirrors
- Sunroof: Panoramic moonroof
- Roof Rails: Available
- Privacy Glass: Available
- Fog Lights: Available

Optional Packages & Upgrades
- Dynamic Pack ($4,500): Includes Configurable Dynamics, Adaptive Dynamics, Red Brake Calipers, and JaguarDrive Control with Adaptive Surface Response
- Performance Seats:
- 14-way power heated and cooled front seats with memory
- 16-way power heated and ventilated massaging front seats with memory
- Interior Options:
- Ebony Suedecloth headlining
- Exterior Options:
- Silver roof rails
- 20-inch 'Style 5031' diamond-turned wheels with gloss grey contrast
- 20-inch 'Style 1067' gloss black wheels

A premium performer, our Accident Free, One Owner, Certified Pre-Owned 2024 Ford Escape ST-Line Select AWD with Tech Pack #2 can power through busy days in Carbonized Gray! Motivated by a TurboCharged 2.0 Liter EcoBoost 4 Cylinder serving up 250hp to an 8 Speed Automatic transmission. This All Wheel Drive SUV also has a sport-tuned suspension for spirited handling, and it sees nearly 31mpg on the highway. Born for bold drivers, our Escape can draw a crowd with its LED lighting, fog lamps, wing-style rear spoiler, black mesh grille, power liftgate, chrome-tipped exhaust outlets, panoramic sunroof, alloy wheels, rear skid plate, and black roof rails.

With Tech Pack #2, our ST-Line Select cabin helps you forget daily hassles by bundling heated power front sport seats, a 13.2-inch touchscreen, a 12.3-inch driver display, connected navigation, wireless charging, and Bang & Olufsen audio. It's a rewarding complement to the heated flat-bottom sport steering wheel, dual-zone automatic climate control, remote start, keyless access/ignition, WiFi compatibility, voice control, and wireless smartphone connectivity.

Drive confidently, knowing Tech Pack #2 adds intelligent Ford features like adaptive cruise control, a digital rearview camera, a 360-degree camera system, and evasive steering to front/rear automatic braking, blind-spot monitoring, forward collision warning, rear cross-traffic alert, lane-keeping assistance, and more. With all that, our Escape ST-Line Select is waiting for your command! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Corwin Ford Tri-City Test Drive Towards Ownership!

As a Ford Gold Certified pre-owned vehicle, this Escape ST-Line Select has undergone a rigorous 172-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty coverage. Enjoy the peace of mind of Roadside Assistance, a $100 deductible, and a transferable warranty, as well as 22,000 FordPass Rewards Points to use towards your first two maintenance visits.

Elevate your driving experience with this meticulously maintained 2024 Ford Escape ST-Line Select. Schedule a test drive today and discover the exceptional quality and performance that awaits you.

Volvo XC90 B5 Plus AWD 2.0L I4 Turbocharged DOHC 16V LEV3-ULEV70 247 Horsepower with 258 lb-ft torque
Comprehensive Airbag System: Includes front, front knee, side, and front & rear curtain airbags. [jdpower.com], [drivedata.org]
Whiplash Protection System (WIPS): Front seat whiplash injury protection. [volvocars.com], [volvocars.com]
Side Impact Protection System (SIPS): Strengthened safety cage and side structure. [volvocars.com], [volvocars.com]
Pedestrian and Cyclist Airbags: External front-end airbag to reduce pedestrian/cyclist injury (on newer trims like 20242026). [volvocars.com], [volvocars.com]

Active & Automated Safety

Forward Collision Warning & Automatic Emergency Braking: With detection of vehicles, pedestrians, cyclists, and large animals (e.g., moose). [volvocars.com], [drivedata.org]
Run-Off-Road Protection & Mitigation: Applies seat belt tensioners, autobraking, and structural safeguards to keep occupants safe. [volvocars.com], [volvocars.com]
Lane Keeping Assist & Lane Departure Warning: Gentle steering assistance if you drift from lane. [drivedata.org], [volvocars.com]
Blind Spot Monitoring: Alerts for vehicles in adjacent lanes. [drivedata.org], [caredge.com]
Cross-Traffic Alert (rear): Warns of approaching traffic while reversing. [jdpower.com]
Adaptive Cruise Control with Pilot Assist: Maintains distance to lead vehicle and provides steering support. [drivedata.org], [jdpower.com]
Automatic High-Beam Assist: Auto-dimming high beams. [jdpower.com]
Driver Monitoring/Attention Alert: Detects signs of drowsiness or distraction. [edmunds.com], [volvonorthfield.com]

Parking & Visibility Aids

Rear Backup Camera & Parking Sensors: Guides with audible alerts when reversing. [jdpower.com], [cars.usnews.com]
360 Surround-View Camera System: (Standard on higher trims or optionally available). [volvocars.com], [volvonorthfield.com]

Vehicle Structural & Lighting Safety

High-Strength Safety Cage: Maintains cabin integrity during impact. [volvocars.com], [volvocars.com]
Advanced LED Headlamps: Auto-leveling, automatic on/off, and adaptive high-beam control for optimized illumination. [jdpower.com], [iihs.org]
Tire Pressure Monitoring System: Monitors real-time tire conditions. [cars.usnews.com], [cars.usnews.com]

Crash Test Recognition

IIHS TOP SAFETY PICK+ Certified: Earned highest safety rating across crashworthiness, crash avoidance, and good-rated headlights. [iihs.org], [volvocars.com]
NHTSA 5-Star Overall Safety Rating: Superior performance in front, side, and rollover resistance. [drivedata.org], [drivedata.org]


These features combine to make the XC90 B5 Plus AWD one of the safest luxury midsize SUVs available. Let me know if you'd like more details on any specific system or comparisons to other models.

Elevate your driving experience with the all-new 2024 Cadillac LYRIQ Tech. This stunning electric crossover offers a bold, distinctive design that commands attention on the road. Beneath the sleek exterior lies a state-of-the-art electric powertrain, delivering a thrilling and efficient driving experience.

The LYRIQ's impressive performance is complemented by an array of advanced technology features. The Google Automotive Services-capable infotainment system provides seamless connectivity, while the Driver Assist Package offers a suite of driver-assistance technologies to enhance your safety and confidence on the road.

Comfort and convenience are also priorities in the LYRIQ. Dual-zone automatic climate control, heated front seats, and a power liftgate ensure a comfortable and convenient driving experience. The premium suspension and 4-wheel disc brakes provide a smooth and responsive ride, while the adaptive cruise control and enhanced automatic parking assist make navigating traffic and parking a breeze.

description:
The 2024 Toyota RAV4 Prime SE is a fully equipped and versatile hybrid SUV featuring a 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine paired with an eCVT transmission and all-wheel drive (AWD). Finished in Midnight Black Metallic with a black cloth interior, it has 27,131 miles on the odometer and is available for sale at Toyota of Portland.

This RAV4 Prime SE comes with a variety of premium features, including a JBL audio system, navigation, a panoramic moonroof, heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a power liftgate. The vehicle also features Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, active cruise control, backup camera, and a TRD package. For safety, it includes blind-spot monitoring, lane departure warning, emergency braking, and rear cross-traffic alert.

The vehicle has been well-maintained with recent services, including oil and filter changes, tire rotations, and brake inspections. It has no reported accidents or damage, and as a Toyota Certified Pre-Owned (CPO) vehicle, it comes with a 7-year/100,000-mile powertrain warranty, 12-month/12,000-mile comprehensive warranty, and 1-year roadside assistance.

For more information or to inquire about purchasing, you can contact Toyota of Portland at (855) 685-1820 or visit their website at https://www.toyotaofportland.com. The dealership is located at 55 NE Broadway St, Portland, OR 97232.

description:
The 2024 Toyota RAV4 Adventure is a well-equipped SUV featuring a 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive (AWD). Finished in Midnight Black Metallic with an artificial leather interior, this vehicle has 47,153 miles on the odometer. It is available for sale as a Toyota Certified Pre-Owned (CPO) vehicle at Toyota of Portland.

This RAV4 Adventure is loaded with premium features, including a JBL audio system, navigation, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, and a power moonroof. For added comfort, it offers heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a remote keyless entry system. It also comes with a backup camera and third-row seating. The vehicle is equipped with a tow package, running boards, and a TRD package, including a TRD Windshield UV Sunshade. For safety, the vehicle includes blind-spot monitoring, lane departure warning, adaptive cruise control, and emergency braking.

The vehicle has been regularly serviced, with recent services including oil and filter changes and tire rotations. The most recent service was completed in January 2026. As a Toyota Certified Pre-Owned (CPO) vehicle, it comes with a 7-year/100,000-mile powertrain warranty, 12-month/12,000-mile comprehensive warranty, and 1-year roadside assistance.

For more information or to inquire about purchasing, you can contact Toyota of Portland at (855) 685-1820 or visit their website at https://www.toyotaofportland.com. The dealership is located at 55 NE Broadway St, Portland, OR 97232.

description:
Experience the future of driving with the exceptional 2024 Kia EV9 Wind. This all-electric SUV offers a captivating blend of cutting-edge technology, uncompromising performance, and unparalleled comfort, making it the perfect choice for the modern, eco-conscious driver.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, the EV9 Wind is designed to elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay, the security of a Backup Camera, and the freedom of All-Wheel Drive. Indulge in the luxury of a Moonroof and the connectivity of Bluetooth Wireless, all while staying effortlessly connected with the intuitive Navigation System.

• Apple CarPlay
• One Owner!
• Back Up Camera
• AWD/4WD/Four Wheel Drive
• Navigation/Nav/GPS
• Moonroof/Sunroof/Roof/Panoramic
• Locally Owned
• Low Miles!
• Bluetooth Wireless
• Carpeted Floor Mat, 7-Passenger
• Folding Cargo Tray

Beneath the sleek exterior lies a powerful electric motor that delivers exhilarating performance, seamlessly propelling you through the city streets or open highways. With the instant torque and responsive handling of the EV9 Wind, you'll experience the true thrill of electric driving.

Designed with your comfort in mind, the EV9 Wind offers a spacious and versatile interior, with ample room for up to seven passengers and their cargo. The split-folding rear seats and Folding Cargo Tray provide exceptional flexibility, ensuring you can adapt to any adventure that comes your way.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the EV9 Wind delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From Automatic Emergency Braking to Lane Departure Warning, you can navigate the roads with confidence, knowing that your safety is our top priority.

As an eco-conscious brand, Kia is committed to a sustainable future, and the EV9 Wind is a testament to that dedication. With its all-electric powertrain and impressive efficiency, you can enjoy the open road while reducing your carbon footprint, making a positive impact on the environment.

Experience the future of driving today. Visit our showroom and discover the exceptional 2024 Kia EV9 Wind. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be captivated by its unparalleled performance, cutting-edge technology, and uncompromising style. Let us help you make the switch to the electric revolution and embark on a journey that's both thrilling and environmentally responsible.

2024 Volvo XC40 Recharge Twin Motor PLUS — New Motors. Bigger Battery. All-Season Confidence. Fresh twin-motors and an upgraded battery give this XC40 sharper response, longer smiles, and that classic Volvo calm that acts like it’s no big deal. Add the Climate Package and suddenly rain, shine, snow, or whatever chaos the forecast cooked up is handled without drama—or even a raised eyebrow. It’s all-electric, wildly capable, and somehow both sensible and mischievous… exactly the kind of trouble Uncle Buck would approve of. PLUS Package Highlights
  • Laminated panoramic roof with power sunshade
  • Foglights and Pixel Technology headlights
  • 360° camera with Park Assist front, rear, and side
  • Air Purifier
  • Power-adjustable passenger seat
  • HomeLink
  • Power-folding rear headrest
  • 12V cargo outlet
Climate Package
  • Heated rear seats
  • Heated steering wheel
  • High-efficiency heat pump
Added Extras
  • Trunk spoiler
  • Protection Package
  • 20" 5-Spoke Black Diamond Cut alloy wheels
Performance
  • Pure electric, zero tailpipe emissions
  • Front and rear electric motors, all-wheel drive
  • 78 kWh lithium-ion high-voltage battery
  • 402 hp and 494 lb-ft torque
  • Shift-by-wire single-speed transmission
  • One-Pedal Drive, electric power-assisted steering
  • ABS with Hill Start Assist
  • 19" alloy wheels (plus optional 20" upgrade listed above)
Audio & Technology
  • 12.3" digital driver display
  • Google built-in: Maps, Assistant, Play Store (4-year subscription)
  • Volvo Cars app remote services: remote start and lock/unlock
  • Inductive smartphone charging, Bluetooth connectivity
  • Over-the-air updates, Apple CarPlay, SiriusXM trial
  • High Performance Sound
  • USB-C ports: 2 front + 2 rear
Safety & Security
  • LED headlights with AHB, DRL, cornering lights and Pixel tech
  • BLIS with Steer Assist and Cross Traffic Alert
  • Collision Avoidance with low/high-speed mitigation (vehicle/pedestrian/cyclist)
  • Driver Alert Control, automatic braking after collision
  • Run-off Road Protection & Mitigation, Lane Keeping Aid, cruise control
  • Front, side, curtain, and driver knee airbags, WHIPS
  • Road Sign Information, Park Assist front, rear, and side
  • Tire repair kit
Luxury & Convenience
  • Laminated panoramic roof with power sunshade
  • Charcoal Fusion Microtech/Textile or Charcoal Connect Suede Textile/Microtech seating
  • Power front seat with driver memory and 4-way power lumbar
  • Mechanical cushion extensions, front seats
  • Heated front seats
  • 2-zone automatic climate control
  • Keyless entry and drive with power operated tailgate
  • Folding load floor with grocery bag holders, glovebox fold-out hook, waste bin in front armrest
  • Power-folding rear headrest, auto-dimming interior and exterior mirrors
  • High-gloss black window decor
Why You’ll Love It
  • New twin-motor setup and battery upgrade for confident acceleration and everyday range
  • Climate Package warmth plus heat pump efficiency for year-round comfort
  • Pixel headlights and 360° camera for brilliant visibility and stress-free parking
Quiet, quick, and cleverly equipped—this XC40 Recharge PLUS makes every mile feel modern.
Its not just a Volvo - Its a Lifestyle


Balance of Factory 4 year/50,000 mile Comprehensive Warranty
w/3 year/36,000 mile Complimentary Scheduled Maintenance
8 year/100,000 miles for limited EV Components



DLR Nordic – Your Trusted Volvo Specialists. Integrity. Excellence.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of rugged capability and refined sophistication with this stunning 2024 Subaru Crosstrek Limited. Meticulously inspected and reconditioned, this Crosstrek is ready to take you on unforgettable adventures while providing the exceptional comfort and convenience you deserve.

Highlighted features include:
• Harman/Kardon Audio & Power Moonroof
• Popular Package #4A
• Rear Bumper Cover
• Splash Guards
• Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror with Approach Light
• Auto-Dimming Mirror with Compass & HomeLink

Powered by a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, this Crosstrek delivers an impressive balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 26 MPG in the city and 33 MPG on the highway.

Step inside and experience the premium cabin, featuring leather-trimmed upholstery, heated front seats, and the advanced STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Plus system with seamless integration for your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The Harman/Kardon surround sound speaker system will elevate your listening experience, while the power moonroof allows you to enjoy the great outdoors.

Versatility is at the heart of the Crosstrek, with a spacious and flexible cargo area that adapts to your needs. The all-weather floor liners and rear bumper cover provide added protection, ensuring your Crosstrek remains in pristine condition, mile after mile.

Safety is paramount, and this Crosstrek is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Subaru's renowned EyeSight Driver Assist Technology, to help keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Discover the perfect balance of capability, comfort, and style with this exceptional 2024 Subaru Crosstrek Limited. Schedule a test drive today and experience the difference for yourself.

The 2024 Subaru Forester Wilderness comes equipped with the following upgrades and options:

• 8" AUDIO W/HARMAN/KARDON & POWER REAR GATE
• Navigation System
• harman/kardon 9-Speaker Audio System
• Panoramic Power Moonroof
• Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel and Shift Knob
• Heated Front Seats
• Textured StarTex Upholstery
• 17" Matte Black Finish Alloy Wheels

This Forester Wilderness is the perfect blend of capability and comfort, designed to take you on all your adventures. With its 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine and Lineartronic CVT, you'll enjoy impressive fuel efficiency of 25 city/28 highway MPG, along with the confidence of Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system.

Inside, the spacious cabin features premium materials and advanced technology, including an 8-inch touchscreen infotainment system with navigation, Harman Kardon premium audio, and seamless smartphone integration. The power rear gate and heated front seats add convenience and comfort, while the rugged yet stylish StarTex upholstery and matte black alloy wheels give the Forester Wilderness a bold, adventurous look.

Whether you're tackling the daily commute or exploring the great outdoors, this Subaru Forester Wilderness is ready to take you there. With its impressive capabilities, premium amenities, and Subaru's renowned reputation for quality and reliability, this vehicle is the perfect choice for the active, adventurous lifestyle.

Subaru Certified Pre-Owned vehicles come with a comprehensive 152-point inspection, Roadside Assistance, and a Powertrain Limited Warranty of 84 months/100,000 miles from the original in-service date. Plus, you'll enjoy a 3-month SiriusXM trial subscription, a $500 Owner Loyalty coupon, and a 1-year trial subscription to STARLINK.

For over 40 years, the Harnish Auto Family has proudly served and serviced Western Washington with trust and excellence! With over 20 acres of inventory to explore, we are confident your perfect ride is waiting for you!

Powered by a robust 2.4L 4-cylinder DOHC engine paired with Subaru's renowned Lineartronic CVT and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, the Ascent Premium delivers a smooth, confident ride with impressive efficiency. Boasting an EPA-estimated 20 city/26 highway MPG, this Ascent will keep you moving with confidence, no matter the road conditions.

Inside, the Ascent Premium pampers you with luxurious touches, including heated front seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a premium STARLINK 11.6" multimedia system with integrated Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The Convenience Package further enhances your driving experience with features like Reverse Automatic Braking, an auto-dimming rearview mirror, and a power liftgate.

With just 12,300 miles on the odometer, this 2024 Subaru Ascent Premium is a true gem. Backed by Subaru's renowned reliability and our Certified Pre-Owned program, you can drive with peace of mind, knowing this vehicle has been meticulously inspected and comes with a comprehensive warranty.

This Jeep is not just your ordinary SUV, it's a game-changer. With its spacious interior, iconic design, and advanced technology, the 2024 Jeep Wrangler Sahara 4xe is ready to take you on any adventure you desire.

Under the hood, the 4xe boasts a hybrid powertrain, featuring a 2.0-liter turbocharged engine paired with two electric motors. This combination delivers an impressive 375 horsepower and 470 lb-ft of torque, giving you the power to conquer any terrain with ease. Plus, with its electric range of up to 25 miles, you can enjoy guilt-free off-roading.

But that's not all, the Sahara 4xe is equipped with the latest safety and technology features to ensure a smooth and safe ride. From blind spot monitoring to adaptive cruise control, the 2024 Jeep Wrangler Sahara 4xe has got you covered.

So why wait? Elevate your driving experience and be the envy of the road with the 2024 Jeep Wrangler Sahara 4xe. Visit your nearest dealership and take a test drive today!

Introducing the 2024 Cadillac XT6 Premium Luxury - a masterful blend of style, technology, and performance that elevates the driving experience. With its striking Opulent Blue Metallic exterior and a wealth of premium features, this certified pre-owned Cadillac is poised to exceed your expectations.

Highlights of this exceptional XT6 include:

• Platinum Package with Semi-Aniline Leather Seating, Sueded Microfiber Headliner, and Performance Suspension
• Super Cruise hands-free driver assistance system
• Technology Package with 8" Color Gauge Cluster, Head-Up Display, and Surround Vision
• Driver Assist Package with Adaptive Cruise Control and Automatic Emergency Braking

The 3.6L V6 engine, paired with a responsive 9-speed automatic transmission and Cadillac's renowned all-wheel-drive system, delivers a thrilling yet refined driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 18 city/25 highway mpg, this XT6 balances power and efficiency, making it a versatile companion for any journey.

Step inside and you'll be enveloped in the premium cabin, featuring genuine wood accents, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and a Bose® Performance Series audio system that will elevate your senses. The spacious, three-row layout provides ample room for passengers and cargo, ensuring everyone travels in comfort.

As a Cadillac Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this XT6 has undergone a rigorous 172-point inspection and reconditioning process. You can drive with confidence, knowing it comes with a 12-month/unlimited-mile limited warranty, 24-hour roadside assistance, and a vehicle history report.

Experience the exceptional craftsmanship and advanced technology of the 2024 Cadillac XT6 Premium Luxury. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this certified pre-owned SUV can elevate your driving experience.

description:
Experience the pinnacle of modern SUV design with the 2024 Kia Sorento X-Pro SX Prestige. This exceptional vehicle is a true masterpiece, blending style, performance, and cutting-edge technology to deliver an unparalleled driving experience.

Under the hood, the Sorento X-Pro SX Prestige boasts a powerful 2.5L I4 DGI Turbocharged DOHC 16V engine, delivering an impressive 281 horsepower and seamlessly paired with an 8-Speed DCT transmission. With its advanced All-Wheel Drive system, you'll conquer any terrain with confidence and ease.

Slip into the driver's seat and be captivated by the Sorento's luxurious interior. Heated and ventilated front bucket seats, a power driver's seat, and a panoramic sunroof create an unparalleled sense of comfort and sophistication. The intuitive 8-inch touchscreen display with navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and in control.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the Sorento X-Pro SX Prestige delivers. This vehicle is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and a Surround View Monitor, ensuring you and your loved ones are protected on every journey.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2024 Kia Sorento X-Pro SX Prestige. This SUV is a true testament to Kia's commitment to innovation, quality, and customer satisfaction. With its exceptional performance, cutting-edge technology, and uncompromising safety, the Sorento X-Pro SX Prestige is the ultimate choice for the discerning driver.

Certified by Stellantis' rigorous quality assurance program, this Sorento X-Pro SX Prestige is ready to provide you with years of reliable and enjoyable driving. Experience the difference that a truly exceptional SUV can make in your life.

The 2024 Subaru Forester Wilderness comes equipped with the following upgrades and options:

• 8" AUDIO W/HARMAN/KARDON & POWER REAR GATE
• Navigation System
• harman/kardon 9-Speaker Audio System
• Panoramic Power Moonroof
• Textured StarTex Upholstery
• Heated Front Bucket Seats

This exceptional Forester Wilderness is the perfect blend of rugged capability and refined comfort. Powered by a 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with Subaru's renowned Lineartronic CVT and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, this SUV delivers an impressive 25 city/28 highway MPG.

The Forester Wilderness truly stands out with its unique Matte Black 17-inch alloy wheels, bold exterior styling, and premium interior features. The 8-inch STARLINK multimedia system with navigation, harman/kardon premium audio, and smartphone integration keeps you connected and entertained on every journey. And with the convenient Power Rear Gate, loading and unloading your gear has never been easier.

Whether tackling the trails or navigating the city streets, the 2024 Subaru Forester Wilderness is a versatile and capable companion. Backed by Subaru's renowned safety and reliability, this SUV is built to take you wherever life's adventures lead.

Subaru Certified Pre-Owned vehicles come with a comprehensive 152-point inspection, Roadside Assistance, a $0 deductible Warranty, and a Powertrain Limited Warranty of 84 months/100,000 miles. Plus, you'll enjoy a 3-month SiriusXM trial subscription, a $500 Owner Loyalty coupon, and a 1-year trial subscription to STARLINK.

For over 40 years, the Harnish Auto Family has proudly served and serviced Western Washington with trust and excellence! With over 20 acres of inventory to explore, we are confident your perfect ride is waiting for you!

Discover the exceptional value and unparalleled features of this 2024 Jeep Grand Cherokee L Limited. This stunning SUV combines rugged capability, refined luxury, and cutting-edge technology, making it the ultimate choice for discerning drivers.

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and equipped with a smooth-shifting 8-speed automatic transmission, this Grand Cherokee L delivers impressive performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 18 city/25 highway MPG. Whether you're navigating the urban jungle or exploring off-road adventures, this 4WD SUV is up to the task.

Step inside and be enveloped in the refined Capri Leatherette interior, complete with ventilated front seats and a dual-pane panoramic sunroof that floods the cabin with natural light. The Luxury Tech Group II package elevates your driving experience with features like the power tilt/telescoping steering column, surround-view camera system, and wireless charging pad.

Safety is a top priority, with advanced systems like the Intersection Collision Assist and ParkSense Front/Rear Park Assist with Stop ensuring you and your loved ones are well-protected on the road. The rearview auto-dimming digital display mirror and rain-sensitive windshield wipers add an extra layer of convenience and peace of mind.

This Jeep Grand Cherokee L Limited is a true gem, with a clean CARFAX report and the backing of Jeep's Certified Pre-Owned program. Enjoy the confidence of a 7-year/100,000-mile limited powertrain warranty, along with the assurance of a 125-point inspection and 24-hour roadside assistance.

This 2024 Audi Q5 Sportback quattro S Line Premium Plus 45 TFSI is a sleek and stylish luxury SUV with 19,273 miles on the odometer. It is powered by a 2.0L turbocharged engine paired with a 7-speed automatic transmission and the quattro all-wheel-drive system. The vehicle comes in a sophisticated black exterior with a leather interior, offering a premium driving experience. It features Audi's MMI Navigation Plus, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration, and a panoramic sunroof. The sound system is a high-quality Bang & Olufsen system with 3D sound, ensuring excellent audio quality.

This Q5 Sportback is equipped with a variety of features, including a power liftgate, adaptive suspension, and a virtual cockpit for a modern, digital driving experience. The vehicle also provides a full suite of safety features such as Audi connect CARE, dynamic steering, emergency communication, and rear parking assist. Inside, the car offers heated and ventilated front seats, leather seating surfaces, and an advanced climate control system.

If you're interested in learning more or scheduling a test drive, you can contact Audi Wilsonville at 26600 SW 95th Ave, Wilsonville, OR 97070. Reach them by phone at 503-217-6440 for any inquiries or to schedule a visit. For further details about the dealership and available vehicles, you can visit their official website at https://www.audiwilsonville.com.

description: This 2024 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon delivers legendary trail-rated capability with the modern tech and safety features drivers want every day. Built to conquer tough terrain, the Rubicon comes equipped with heavy-duty axles, locking differentials, a disconnecting sway bar, and Jeeps proven four-wheel-drive system ready for rocks, snow, sand, and everything in between. The Technology Group brings the Wrangler firmly into the modern age with advanced infotainment, integrated navigation and connectivity, and intuitive controls that make every drive easier, whether you're heading off the grid or commuting around town. The Safety Group adds an extra layer of confidence with advanced driver-assist features designed to help protect you and your passengers on every journey. Topping it all off is the desirable 3-piece hard top, giving you the flexibility to enjoy open-air driving when the weathers right while still providing the quiet ride, insulation, and security of a hard top year-round. With four doors and plenty of usable cargo space, this Rubicon balances serious off-road performance with everyday practicality. If you're looking for an iconic SUV that blends uncompromising capability, modern technology, and real-world comfort, this 2024 Jeep Wrangler Rubicon is ready to deliver on the trail, on the highway, and everywhere in between. See it today at Carter Subaru in Shoreline. Come shop at Carter Subaru Today!

Ourisman Honda of Fredrick is proud to present the 2024 Honda CR-V Hybrid Sport-L
The 2024 Honda CR-V Hybrid Sport-L brings together sleek styling, hybrid efficiency, and a premium interior for a balanced driving experience. The exterior is highlighted by a bold blacked-out grille, LED headlights and taillights, 18-inch Berlina Black alloy wheels, and sporty design accents that set it apart from the standard CR-V. Power comes from a 2.0L Atkinson-cycle 4-cylinder engine paired with two electric motors, producing 204 horsepower on a AWD drivetrain for smooth acceleration and impressive fuel efficiency. The cabin is refined with leather-trimmed seating, heated front seats, a power-adjustable driver's seat with memory, and a spacious rear seating area. Technology is modern and intuitive, featuring a 9-inch touchscreen with wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, a 320-watt 8-speaker audio system, and wireless phone charging. Safety and driver assistance are well-covered with Honda Sensing, which includes adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assist, blind-spot monitoring, and collision mitigation braking. For those who want an efficient hybrid SUV that blends sporty style with premium comfort and advanced tech, the 2024 Honda CR-V Hybrid Sport-L delivers a confident and well-rounded package.

Equipment

This 2024 Ford Explorer features cruise control for long trips. This Ford Explorer features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. Keep your hands warm all winter with a heated steering wheel in the Ford Explorer . Quickly unlock this Ford Explorer with keyless entry. Enjoy the convenience of the power liftgate on this 1/2 ton suv. The state of the art park assist system will guide you easily into any spot. Start the vehicle from inside with remote start.

Packages

Additional Information

description: Experience refined luxury and dynamic performance with the 2021 BMW X5 xDrive40i, a sophisticated midsize luxury SUV that perfectly blends comfort, technology, and power. Under the hood, the X5 xDrive40i boasts a 3.0-liter BMW TwinPower Turbo inline-six engine paired with an intelligent all-wheel drive system, delivering a smooth yet responsive driving experience in various road conditions. The vehicle presents a sleek, modern exterior with bold lines and an imposing presence, while the available panoramic sunroof and dual sunroof setup flood the well-appointed cabin with natural light, enhancing the sense of spaciousness and connection to the outside environment.----Inside, the X5 xDrive40i surrounds passengers with premium materials and advanced features. Supple leather seats offer a luxurious feel and exceptional comfort for both driver and passengers. The integrated navigation system ensures seamless journeys, easily guiding you to your destination, while Apple CarPlay compatibility allows for intuitive smartphone integration to access your favorite apps and media on the go. Safety is front and center with advanced driver assistance technologies, including a forward collision warning system that alerts the driver to potential hazards ahead. description: The 2021 BMW X5 M50i xDrive is a high-performance luxury SUV that blends power, sophistication, and advanced technology into one commanding package. Under the hood, it features a robust 4.4-liter BMW M TwinPower Turbo V8 engine, delivering a thrilling 523 horsepower and 553 lb-ft of torque, paired with an intelligent xDrive all-wheel-drive system for confident control in all conditions. The exterior design is sleek and athletic, while the interior provides outstanding comfort with leather-trimmed seats and premium materials throughout. A panoramic sunroof enhances the cabin's spacious feel, flooding it with natural light and offering scenic views.----Inside, the X5 M50i is equipped with advanced technology to elevate both convenience and safety. The state-of-the-art navigation system offers real-time traffic updates and intuitive controls, while the Wi-Fi hotspot keeps passengers connected on the go. Audio quality is exceptional, thanks to the premium sound system that delivers crisp, immersive sound throughout the cabin. For peace of mind, the SUV includes a Collision Warning system that helps detect potential hazards and can apply emergency braking if needed. Overall, the 2021 BMW X5 M50i xDrive is a superb choice for those seeking exhilarating performance, luxurious amenities, and cutting-edge safety features in a versatile and stylish SUV.

2021 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon 4WD

3.6L V6 • Rubicon Off-Road Package • 4WD • Tuscadero Pearlcoat

This 2021 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Rubicon is the real dealfactory-equipped with legendary off-road capability, modern technology, and bold styling. Finished in the rare and highly desirable Tuscadero Pearlcoat with a Black interior, this Rubicon stands out everywhere it goes. Power comes from Jeeps proven 3.6L V6 paired with a smooth 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering dependable performance on the trail or the highway.

With just 36,210 miles, this Wrangler Rubicon has seen limited use and remains a strong, clean example of one of the most capable SUVs on the market. Whether youre hitting the trails, cruising with the top off, or tackling winter conditions, this Wrangler is built to handle it all.

Rubicon Performance & Capability:

3.6L V6 24V VVT Engine

8-Speed Automatic Transmission

4WD with Rock-Trac Transfer Case

Front & rear locking differentials

Electronic sway-bar disconnect

Heavy-duty Dana 44 axles

Off-road-tuned suspension

Skid plates and rock rails

Interior & Comfort Features:

Rubicon-specific interior trim

Heated front seats

Heated steering wheel

Push-button start

Keyless entry

Power windows and locks

Fold-down rear seats for added cargo space

Technology & Safety:

Touchscreen infotainment system

Apple CarPlay & Android Auto

Bluetooth hands-free connectivity

Backup camera

Blind-spot monitoring

Rear cross-path detection

Stability and traction control

Exterior Highlights:

Tuscadero Pearlcoat rare, bold, and highly sought after

Rubicon hood with functional vents

Factory alloy wheels with all-terrain tires

Removable doors and roof

Iconic Wrangler design

Why Buy From Us?

Family-owned and operated since 1980

Two convenient Lynnwood locations

Transparent, pressure-free buying experience

4.6+ Google rating with thousands of satisfied customers

Financing available for all credit types
